# game/Kyou 10.rpy:631
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_44bcfa72:

    # ks "And I don't really get it either. I don't get how just telling you how good it feels to be hypnotized makes you into some kind of... I dunno, an addict?" with dissolve
    ks "Y yo tampoco lo entiendo del todo. No entiendo cómo tan solo decirte lo bien que se siente estar hipnotizada puede convertirte en alguna clase de... No sé, ¿adicta?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:633
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_71c4db98:

    # s "Don't call me that again." with dissolve
    s "No vuelvas a llamarme así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:634
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0bf820b2:

    # ks neutral blush "Yeah, sorry."
    ks neutral blush "Sí, perdón."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:636
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ca6d6b78:

    # s "But how do you propose to help me? More hypnosis?" with dissolve
    s "Pero ¿cómo propones ayudarme? ¿Más hipnosis?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:637
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_56c3ac0c:

    # "She tries to hide it, but she can't disguise the hopeful lilt in her voice."
    "Intenta ocultarlo, pero no puede disimular el entusiasmo en su voz."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:639
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2e3596ce:

    # ks sigh noblush "Yeah. I mean, if I put you into this state, I could try to take you out again?" with dissolve
    ks sigh noblush "Sí. Bueno, si yo te puse en ese estado, podría intentar sacarte." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:641
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_72d883b7:

    # s "I do not know if my desires are taking over or if I truly believe this is a sensible course of action given what has happened, but... yes, I would permit you to try." with dissolve
    s "No sé si es mi deseo el que está hablando, o si en verdad creo que es una decisión sensata dado lo que ha ocurrido, pero... sí, te permitiré intentarlo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:644
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_94af2503:

    # s "However, there is something else I would like you to do." with dissolve
    s "No obstante, hay algo más que quisiera que hagas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:645
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_19efb262:

    # ks neutral "What's that?"
    ks neutral "¿Qué cosa?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:646
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2538006d:

    # "Sayori reaches into her pocket to pull out her phone, then swipes her fingers over the screen as she talks."
    "Sayori saca su teléfono del bolsillo, luego continúa hablando mientras desliza sus dedos por la pantalla."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:648
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2d2298f3:

    # s "My inability to remember our hypnosis sessions is an issue. And I am going to trust you have not made any particular effort to make it so." with dissolve
    s "Mi incapacidad de recordar nuestras sesiones de hipnosis es un problema. Y confío en que no has hecho ningún esfuerzo en particular para que así suceda." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:649
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_3c6366ea:

    # ks "Y-yeah, not at all. It's not uncommon for people to forget the trances."
    ks "S-sí, ninguno. No es raro que la gente olvide los trances."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:650
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f9956746:

    # s "Understood."
    s "Entiendo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:651
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8f6842ec:

    # "She then hands me her phone, which seems to be open on a video app."
    "Después me entrega su teléfono, el cual parece tener la aplicación de video abierta."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:653
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_85c45562:

    # s "Then I need you to record our session. I want to know of everything that happens when you hypnotize me with that penlight of yours." with dissolve
    s "Entonces necesito que grabes nuestra sesión. Quiero saber todo lo que pasa cuando me hipnotizas con tu linterna." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:655
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b9af0510:

    # s "I believe it will turn out to be useful." with dissolve
    s "Considero que será de utilidad." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:656
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9e820a7a:

    # "I take the phone from her and nod as I turn its camera towards her face with one hand..."
    "Tomo su teléfono asintiendo y apunto la cámara hacia su rostro con una mano."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:659
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ef5ca358:

    # "... While raising my penlight aloft with the other."
    "... Mientras sostengo mi linterna en lo alto con la otra."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:660
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c18fca6a:

    # ks smile "Sure. So I'm going to try and convince your subconscious to let go of how \"wonderful\" hypnosis feels."
    ks smile "Claro. Entonces intentaré convencer a tu subconsciente de dejar de pensar que la hipnosis se siente \"maravillosa\"."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:662
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0f15205a:

    # s "Not just that, Kyou." with dissolve
    s "No solo eso, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:663
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_6dffe5c4:

    # ks surprised "Huh?"
    ks surprised "¿Eh?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:665
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e7ce5ee9:

    # s "I need you to try to remove everything we have worked on together. The sleep inducement, the leg numbness... all of it." with dissolve
    s "Necesito que intentes remover todo en lo que emos trabajado juntos. La inducción al sueño, el entumecimiento de piernas... todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:666
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_900bbcf0:

    # s "I need you to be thorough."
    s "Necesito que seas exhaustivo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:668
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_df2dd5c1:

    # s "Because if I cannot trust my own thoughts after this is over, then..." with dissolve
    s "Porque si no puedo confiar en mis propios pensamientos cuando esto termine, yo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:670
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8cd34535:

    # "Sayori trails off, and yeah. I get it."
    "Sayori corta su oración, y sí. Entiendo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:671
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_67b5362f:

    # "She's scared."
    "Está asustada."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:672
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_78779f7d:

    # "I'd have wanted her to keep hold of the sleep hypnosis at least. It seemed to have helped her so much."
    "Habría querido que conservara por lo menos lo de dormir. Parece haberla ayudado mucho."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:673
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4b24d937:

    # "But if it means she's going to suffer like this during the day then maybe this is for the best."
    "Pero si eso significa que sufrirá tanto durante el día, puede que esto sea para mejor."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:674
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2f01a8e6:

    # "I don't want Sayori to suffer."
    "No quiero que Sayori sufra."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:675
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2483a8d5:

    # ks smile "Sure. So that's what I'm going to do."
    ks smile "Claro. Entonces eso es lo que haré."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:679
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_250e8800:

    # "Sayori's eyes instinctually look up towards the light in my hand as I pass it over her eyes once again."
    "Los ojos de Sayori voltean instintivamente a ver la luz que hay en mi mano, la cual, una vez más, deslizo por sus ojos."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:680
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7e1a9ee0:

    # "Wow, she really is fixated on this thing now."
    "Guau, en serio está obsesionada con esta cosa."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:681
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7333f7ce:

    # ks "And all you need to do, Sayori, is relax and focus. Just like before."
    ks "Y lo único que tienes que hacer, Sayori, es relajarte y concentrarte. Justo así."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:685
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_6b267e91:

    # s "U-uhh, yes... focus..."
    s "E-eeh, sí... concentrarme..."

translate spanish strings:

    # game/Kyou 10.rpy:527
    old "Prove to her that she wants this (Outline only)"
    new "Demostrarle que esto es lo que quiere (Bosquejo únicamente)"

# TODO: Translation updated at 2020-10-30 23:16

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:519
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2d661c24:

    # ks angry "But if that's true, if... if you think I'm that shit then why help me at all?"
    ks angry "Pero si eso es verdad, si... si también crees que soy un jodido trozo basura, ¿por qué ayudarme?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:553
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4f6272b0:

    # s alert_sleeptalk_concerned blush "I cannot understand what is happening to me." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk_concerned blush "No comprendo lo que me está pasando." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:557
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_fbc2d04f:

    # ks "O-okay, let's... sit down and talk this through, okay?"
    ks "M-muy bien, hay que... sentarnos y discutámoslo, ¿de acuerdo? "

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:568
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d004ae85:

    # s "I have turned it over in my mind so many times, and I have found it difficult to dispute your reasoning."
    s "Le he dado vueltas en la cabeza tantas veces, y sin embargo me ha sido difícil disputar tu razonamiento."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:575
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f15e5531:

    # s "It is difficult to accept, but..." with dissolve
    s "Es difícil de aceptar, pero..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:576
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e30ea539:

    # s "To think I would actually find such pleasure in our shared activity."
    s "Pensar que experimentaría tal placer durante nuestra actividad."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:583
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7ef65d48:

    # s "So this deep need has been buried within me for all this time, that you merely brought to light?" with dissolve
    s "¿Acaso este menester ha estado sepultado en mi interior todo este tiempo, y tú simplemente lo sacaste a la luz por mí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:585
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_fbe88fd0:

    # s "And that is why your earlier therapy was so profoundly effective?" with dissolve
    s "¿Y es por eso que tu terapia fue tan profundamente efectiva?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:619
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ef4efae4:

    # s "So Kyou, answer me... have I been foolish to consider that my subconscious desire was altered unnaturally? Forcefully?" with dissolve
    s "Así que, Kyou, respóndeme... ¿estoy siendo tonta al pensar que mis deseos subconscientes fueron alterados de manera antinatural? ¿A la fuerza?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:622
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4fc4e630:

    # s "That I..." with dissolve
    s "Que yo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:625
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b8d176b1:

    # "Damn, I think I'm blushing along with her when she phrases it like that."
    "Diablos, cuando lo pone así, creo que me hace sonrojarme tanto como ella."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:643
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d42850c9:

    # s "But how do you propose to assist me? With more hypnosis?" with dissolve
    s "Pero ¿cómo propones asistirme? ¿Con más hipnosis?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:648
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_81c25515:

    # s "I do not know if my desires are taking over or if I truly believe this a sensible course of action given what has transpired, but... yes, I would permit you to try." with dissolve
    s "No sé si es mi deseo el que está hablando, o si en verdad creo que es una decisión sensata dado lo que ha ocurrido, pero... sí, te permitiré intentarlo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:655
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c37ccf14:

    # s "My inability to remember our hypnosis sessions is problematic, to say the least." with dissolve
    s "Mi incapacidad de recordar nuestras sesiones de hipnosis es, cuanto menos, problemática." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:656
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9c103924:

    # s "And I am going to trust you have not made any particular effort to make it so."
    s "Y confío en que no has hecho ningún esfuerzo en particular pera que así suceda."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:661
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_cf6d4e7d:

    # s "Then I need you to record what we do tonight. I want to know of everything that happens when you hypnotize me with that penlight of yours." with dissolve
    s "Entonces necesito que grabes lo que hagamos esta noche. Quiero saber todo lo que pase cuando me hipnotices con tu linterna." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:674
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_380045c4:

    # s "I need you to remove everything we have worked on together. Or at least make the attempt." with dissolve
    s "Necesito que remuevas todo en lo que hemos trabajado juntos. O por lo menos hacer el intento." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:676
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d749944f:

    # s "The sleep inducement, the numbing of my lower limbs... all of it." with dissolve
    s "La inducción al sueño, el entumecimiento de mis extremidades inferiores... todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:678
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_01a71b17:

    # s "I need you to be thorough. Because if I cannot trust my own thoughts after this is over, then..." with dissolve
    s "Necesito que seas exhaustivo. Porque si no puedo confiar en mis propios pensamientos cuando esto termine, yo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:680
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c3652258:

    # "Sayori trails off, and yeah. I get it. She's scared."
    "Sayori corta su oración, y sí, entiendo. Está asustada."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:696
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_06d7f018:

    # ks "That's right. There's no need to think of anything else."
    ks "Eso es. No hace falta pensar en nada más."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:698
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_67fb3a82:

    # ks "Just relax and focus. Letting the light pass over you."
    ks "Solo relájate y concéntrate. Deja que la luz te guíe."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:700
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5267df84:

    # ks "Thoughts fading..."
    ks "Que tus pensamientos se desvanezcan..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:704
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_1ee4984b:

    # ks "Eyes drooping..."
    ks "Y tus ojos caigan..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:708
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a1818f26:

    # ks "Just letting it all happen so naturally. So peacefully."
    ks "Es muy natural dejar que ocurra. Sentir esa paz."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:712
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_6421c4ed:

    # ks neutral "That's right, Sayori. Deep asleep now."
    ks neutral "Eso es, Sayori. Ahora duerme profundamente."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:715
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_397a296f:

    # "I almost didn't have to try at all this time."
    "Esta vez apenas tuve que intentarlo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:716
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_450421c8:

    # ks "Going so very deep for me. Becoming so much more relaxed..."
    ks "Déjate caer muy profundo. Siente esa relajación..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:717
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a6fb09d3:

    # "But I can't slack off."
    "Pero no puedo bajar el ritmo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:718
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f62b3314:

    # ks "Letting the last of your conscious thoughts leave your mind so effortlessly..."
    ks "Siente lo fácil que es dejar que hasta el último pensamiento consciente se vaya..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:719
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_298ad84a:

    # "I need to make sure her subconscious will unlearn what I taught it."
    "Tengo que asegurarme de que su subconsciente desaprenda lo que le enseñé."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:720
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b1e2bbde:

    # ks "Feeling so wonderful."
    ks "Se siente maravilloso."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:721
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f662b050:

    # "... Dammit, that's not helpful. I was supposed to avoid that word."
    "... Maldita sea, eso no ayuda. Se suponía que evitara esa palabra."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:722
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4acf52b9:

    # "Well, never mind. Hopefully it won't matter after we're finished."
    "Bueno, ¿ya qué? Con suerte no importará cuando hayamos terminado."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:723
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c0ab8796:

    # "Taking a breath to collect myself, I keep her phone steadily pointed at her rested form as I consider my next words."
    "Respirando hondo para calmarme, sostengo firmemente su teléfono, apuntando a su sosegado rostro, mientras considero mis próximas palabras."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:724
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b0757374:

    # ks "So now that you're so very relaxed. So very deep in subconscious thought, I need you to listen very carefully to what I'm about to tell you."
    ks "Y ahora que estás tan relajada. Tan sumida en tu subconsciente, necesito que escuches con mucho cuidado lo que estoy por decirte."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:725
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d3a2f764:

    # ks "And what I am telling you is... you need to think back to the times we spent together, all the other times you were in this deep state of hypnosis..."
    ks "Y voy a decirte que... debes recordar esos momentos que pasamos juntos, esas otras veces en las que estuviste en este profundo estado de hipnosis..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:726
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7802ef6e:

    # ks "... Think back and realize that nothing I said to you while you were hypnotized will affect your behaviour or way of thinking any longer."
    ks "... Recuerda y date cuenta de que nada de lo que te dije mientras estuviste hipnotizada seguirá afectando tu comportamiento ni tus pensamientos de ninguna forma."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:727
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_89af31ca:

    # ks "When I told you hypnosis feels so utterly wonderful? There's no need to think like that. You will decide for yourself how hypnosis feels to you."
    ks "¿Cuando te dije lo plenamente maravillosa que la hipnosis se siente? No hace falta pensar así. Tú misma decidirás cómo se siente."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:728
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_fc743887:

    # ks "And when I told you how your legs and feet become detatched from your body whenever I say \"book dumb\", and restore themselves when I say \"book smart\"?"
    ks "¿Y cuando te dije que tus piernas y pies se desprenderían de tu cuerpo cuando dijera \"burro\" y que se reconectarían cuando dijera \"cerebrito\"?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:729
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4643fad1:

    # ks "You will find those words no longer instill any compulsions in you, Sayori. Whether spoken by me or anyone else."
    ks "Notarás que esas palabras ya no imponen ningún impulso sobre ti, Sayori. Así las diga yo o quien sea."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:730
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8aa8e74e:

    # "I let out a quiet sigh before getting to the final part."
    "Dejo salir un silencioso suspiro antes de comenzar con la última parte."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:731
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5c7918e0:

    # ks "Also, when I said to you that your mind will become blank and you'll fall into a deep sleep whenever you settle in your bed at night?"
    ks "Y también, ¿cuando dije tus pensamientos se apagarían y caerías en un profundo sueño siempre que te fueras a la cama por las noches?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:732
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_3f63ada5:

    # ks "You will no longer feel any differently from how you used to. How you decide to spend your time in bed is completely up to you."
    ks "Ya no te sentirás diferente a como solías sentirte. Como decidas pasar tu tiempo en cama depende completamente de ti."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:733
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_1a68d8c1:

    # "There. Now to wrap things up and see how she feels now."
    "Listo. Hora de terminar y ver cómo se siente."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:734
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_439ff447:

    # ks "And finally... Anything else I may have said to you during your time in hypnosis, anything that may have influenced your thinking in any way will no longer apply."
    ks "Y finalmente… Cualquier otra cosa que pueda haberte dicho mientras estabas hipnotizada, que pueda influenciar tu pensamiento de cualquier forma, ya no aplicará."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:735
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9e299e28:

    # ks "Anything you do, or say, or think, will be entirely your own choice."
    ks "Todo lo que hagas, o digas, o pienses, será tu propia decisión."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:736
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a595a686:

    # ks "Understand, Sayori?"
    ks "¿Comprendes, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:737
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_aad8e45e:

    # "There's a short pause as her lips sleepily part in reply."
    "Hay una pausa en lo que sus labios lentamente se separan para responder."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:739
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_479fca87:

    # s "Uh-huh... I understand..." with dissolve
    s "Ajá... Comprendo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:742
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_daeefb49:

    # ks "That's won-... That's great, Sayori. Now we're going to wake you up from this state of hypnosis and back to conscious thought."
    ks "Marav-... Grandioso, Sayori. Ahora vamos a despertarte de este estado de hipnosis y volverás a pensar de manera consciente."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:743
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f043ed6b:

    # ks "Slowly. Gradually. On a count of five, okay?"
    ks "Lentamente. Gradualmente. A la cuenta de cinco, ¿está bien?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:745
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_bc1063a4:

    # s "Okay..." with dissolve
    s "Bien..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:748
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5d0430d2:

    # ks "Starting now with... one. Letting yourself take a nice deep breath, feeling all that relaxation in your body."
    ks "Comenzando ahora con... uno. Respira muy profundo, sintiendo toda esa relajación en tu cuerpo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:749
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_36e635c1:

    # ks "Two. Letting some of that relaxation slip away now. Another breath..."
    ks "Dos. Deja que un poco de esa relajación disminuya. Toma aire otra vez..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:750
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e0fff54d:

    # "I watch as her chest gently rises at my say so."
    "Observo cómo su pecho se eleva gentilmente a mi señal."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1830
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7fdcb9da:

    # "Should I be worried that even after my attempt to deprogram her she's still super responsive to my instructions?"
    "¿Debería preocuparme que, incluso después de intentar desprogramarla, siga siendo tan responsiva a mis instrucciones?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:752
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4bbad432:

    # ks "Three. Strength returning to your limbs. Becoming more aware, more awake, more alert..."
    ks "Tres. La fuerza regresa a tus extremidades. Cada vez más consciente, más despierta, más alerta..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:753
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_cbc5a6fb:

    # "Ugh, let's not think about that for now."
    "Aj, no pensemos en eso por ahora."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:754
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a353ff32:

    # ks "Four. Letting your head rise. Breathing again, freely and easily, eyelids feeling lighter; conscious thoughts returning..."
    ks "Cuatro. Deja que tu cabeza se levante. Respirando de nuevo con total libertad. Tus párpados se sienten más ligeros. Tus pensamientos conscientes regresan..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:757
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4d91c4fa:

    # "I smile at Sayori as her head straightens on my direction."
    "Le sonrío a Sayori, viendo cómo su cabeza se fortalece a mi dirección."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:758
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_32ea78b3:

    # "Really hope she'll start to feel more like herself now."
    "En verdad espero que con esto empiece a sentirse más como ella misma."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:760
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_359b2806:

    # ks smile "And five, Sayori... {nw}"
    ks smile "Y cinco, Sayori... {nw}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:763
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a4c15b17:

    # extend "{w=0.5}Eyes open, wide awake and refreshed."
    extend "{w=0.5}Ojos abiertos, fresca y despierta."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:764
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c0d0c45e:

    # "Sayori breathes deeply as her head sways gently in sleepy confusion."
    "Sayori respira hondo, balanceando suavemente su cabeza en soñolienta confusión."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:766
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f119d1ec:

    # "She barely registers the touch of her phone as I return it to her hand."
    "Apenas se percata del tacto de su teléfono cuando vuelvo a ponerlo en su mano."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:767
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_02ef6377:

    # s "Mrrn... {w=0.5}{nw}"
    s "Mmnn... {w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:770
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_918af714:

    # extend "{cps=10}A-ahh.{/cps}"
    extend "{cps=10}A-aah.{/cps}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:771
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_172691a0:

    # "Although when she does, it seems to comfort her as her fingers close around it and her eyes begin to focus on my face."
    "Aunque, cuando se da cuenta, parece darle consuelo, pues sus dedos se cierran sobre él y sus ojos comienzan a enfocarse en mi rostro."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:773
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_68ec18f3:

    # ks "Welcome back."
    ks "Bienvenida de vuelta."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:775
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_23f825fd:

    # s "K-Kyou... What happened?" with dissolve
    s "K-Kyou... ¿Qué sucedió?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:776
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c29c73fe:

    # ks "I did exactly what you asked. Nothing we did during your trances should affect you now."
    ks "Hice exactamente lo que pediste. Nada de lo que hicimos durante tus trances debería afectarte ahora."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:777
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e06627e2:

    # "I declare it authoritively, to try and put her uncertainty at ease."
    "Lo declaro de forma autoritaria para intentar calmar su incertidumbre."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:778
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b72d589e:

    # "But I can feel the smile fade from my face somewhat as Sayori looks to her phone, still recording footage."
    "Pero puedo sentir la sonrisa difuminarse un poco en mi rostro mientras Sayori mira su teléfono, el cual sigue grabando."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:780
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_fb3394c6:

    # s "Of course." with dissolve
    s "Desde luego." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:781
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8fd9ded0:

    # "I guess we can't be so sure until tomorrow, at least."
    "Supongo que no podemos estar seguros, al menos hasta mañana."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1861
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_60b0f42e:

    # "But what happens now? It seems neither of us is willing to answer in the moment as we share a discomforting silence."
    "Pero ¿qué ocurrirá ahora? Parece que ninguno de los dos piensa responder de momento, y el incómodo silencio se prolonga."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:783
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_1bdbcce4:

    # "Finally, Sayori glances over her phone's screen and runs her thumb over it to turn off the video, then nods to me."
    "Finalmente, Sayori dirige su mirada a la pantalla del teléfono y desliza su dedo para apagar la grabación, luego asiente."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:785
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_fa9f2191:

    # s "Thank you, Kyou. For honouring my request." with dissolve
    s "Gracias, Kyou. Por cumplir con mi petición." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:786
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_56898522:

    # s "But I think I should go."
    s "Pero creo que debo irme."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:792
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_21348d81:

    # s "I need to think about..."
    s "Necesito pensar en..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:793
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4ab7960c:

    # "As she rises unsteadily to her feet, Sayori hugs herself, phone still in hand as she lets out a weary sigh."
    "Poniéndose de pie con inseguridad, Sayori se abraza, con su teléfono aún en mano, y suelta un fatigado suspiro."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:796
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_cc10a3ff:

    # s "S-So many things..." with dissolve
    s "M-muchísimas cosas…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:803
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ad3b235c:

    # "I watch her quietly as she lets herself out...."
    "La veo salir en silencio..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:945
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_11cb7d0b:

    # "... And I'm left to think about everything over dinner."
    "... Y me quedo solo, pensando en todo mientras ceno."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:946
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0228b4ba:

    # "Noodles again. Dad's the cook around here and I didn't think to hit the convenience store while I was worried about Sayori."
    "Fideos otra vez. Papá es el cocinero aquí y no se me ocurrió ir a la tienda de conveniencia con la preocupación que sentía por Sayori."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:948
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_dbe3d5a8:

    # "Did I... Did my hypnosis on her really affect her that much?"
    "¿Acaso yo... acaso mi hipnosis de verdad la afectó tanto?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:949
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_10228d6f:

    # "Have I seriously been brainwashing her?"
    "¿En serio le estaba lavando el cerebro?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:952
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f8cc0e76:

    # "... With this?"
    "... ¿Con esto?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:953
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_1dde6056:

    # "Thinking how my little side project could possibly unlock the human mind as fully as Sayori seemed to think I did. It seems ridiculous."
    "Pensar que mi pequeño proyecto personal pueda desbloquear la mente humana tan a fondo como dijo Sayori. Parece ridículo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:954
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_79196bb9:

    # "But I can't imagine Sayori to be the kind of person to say something like that if she didn't believe it."
    "Pero no me imagino a Sayori diciendo algo así si no lo creyera."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:956
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9755f740:

    # "It makes me feel numb, thinking I could have that kind of power over a girl like her."
    "Me siento entumecido de solo pensar que podría tener esa clase de poder sobre una chica como ella."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:957
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_bbbfc071:

    # "And that I just gave it up?"
    "¿Y renuncié a él?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:958
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8812fc3e:

    # "Shit, what am I even doing right now? What kind of thought was THAT?!"
    "Mierda, ¿y ahora qué estoy haciendo? ¡¿Por qué estoy pensando en ESO?! "

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:959
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e064aef8:

    # "I'm so fucking confused. What do I do with myself?"
    "Estoy tan confundido. ¿Qué carajos hago ahora?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:962
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d768f64f:

    # "What do I do with you?"
    "¿Qué hago contigo?"

# TODO: Translation updated at 2020-11-15 11:06

translate spanish strings:

    # game/Kyou 10.rpy:527
    old " (disabled)Prove to her that she wants this"
    new "Demostrarle que esto es lo que quiere"
