# game/Kyou 10.rpy:337
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d467793f:

    # "Well... at least that's over. Man what a bust."
    "Bueno... al menos eso se acabó. Caray, qué desastre."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:339
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a075794b:

    # "I'm glad those were just the mock exams because that was brutal. And I don't want to think about what'll happen when it's time for the real thing..."
    "Me alegra que solo hayan sido simulacros, porque eso estuvo brutal. Y no quiero ni pensar en lo que pasará cuando sea hora de hacer los de verdad..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:340
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_47b606c7:

    # "But in my defence I had a lot of distractions."
    "Pero en mi defensa tuve muchas distracciones."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:350
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_16c651d0:

    # "Distractions that I notice just walked out of the classroom..."
    "Distracciones que, me doy cuenta, acaban de salir caminando del salón..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:351
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ef6dbb98:

    # s "Did you really find it so difficult?"
    s "¿En serio les pareció tan complicado?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:352
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_223df1e9:

    # n sad_side "Yeah. I don't know why it was so hard, but I saw a lot of those questions and my mind just went blank." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Seh. No sé por qué fue tan difícil, pero vi muchas de esas preguntas y mi mente se puso en blanco." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:351
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_82d4d190:

    # h confused_side "Maybe if you could've seen the questions better?" with dissolve
    h confused_side "¿Tal vez si pudieras ver las preguntas mejor?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:356
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_10bd8d65:

    # n irritated "I told you I'm not THAT near-sighted." with dissolve
    n irritated "Ya te dije que no estoy TAN miope." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:360
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_403c7740:

    # n "... Just needed to squint a little bit." with dissolve
    n "... Solo tuve que entrecerrar los ojos un poquito." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:362
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cc2184d4:

    # s rolleyes "Oh, come on Nozomi, you had ample time to fix your frames had you not invested in this foolish school performance." with dissolve
    s rolleyes "Oh, vamos Nozomi, tuviste tiempo de sobra para arreglar tus armazones de no haberte involucrado en ese bobo espectáculo escolar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:363
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0475afef:

    # h frown_side "H'yeah, well it ain't her fault if the school's gonna make us do Q 'n' A in the middle of fuckin' culture fest." with dissolve
    h frown_side "Sí, pues no es su culpa que la escuela nos ponga a contestar preguntas en medio de un puto festival cultural." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:365
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_12ab44c1:

    # s "You all knew well in advance that this was coming. Perhaps if you had just a little foresight to plan ahead instead of indulging in this spontaneity." with dissolve
    s "Ambas sabían con anticipación que esto estaba por venir. Quizás da haber tenido solo un poco de previsión para planear en vez de comprometerse a esto espontáneamente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:366
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c2d8d842:

    # s irritated "If you cannot handle the additional responsibility, you can always follow the rest of the class and help with the café." with dissolve
    s irritated "Si no pueden con la responsabilidad adicional, siempre pueden seguir al resto de la clase y ayudar con el café." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:368
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f6341b8f:

    # n "We can handle it, Sayori!" with dissolve
    n "¡Podemos con esto, Sayori!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:369
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a4a78f7a:

    # s uniform_folded "The evidence suggests otherwise." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded "La evidencia sugiere lo contrario." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:370
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_81296747:

    # h uniform_armup irritated "Man, will you let it go already? You sound mad." with dissolve
    h uniform_armup irritated "Caray, ¿quieres parar ya con eso? Suenas molesta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:371
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_63b53fb1:

    # s uniform sleeptalk "No. Merely disappointed in you both." with dissolve
    s uniform sleeptalk "No. Meramente decepcionada de las dos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:373
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ce5d16b7:

    # h furious_side "That's fuckin' worse and you know it!" with dissolve
    h furious_side "¡Esa mierda es peor y lo sabes!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:374
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_61330c15:

    # n sad "Uh... hello, Kyou." with dissolve
    n sad "Em... hola, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:377
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_18afcab8:

    # "Just then Nozomi offers a greeting as she notices me standing nearby." with dissolve
    "En ese momento, Nozomi me ofrece un saludo al darse cuenta de que estoy parado en la cercanía." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:378
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b48b0954:

    # h frown "Yeah, hi. You just gonna stand there or what?" with dissolve
    h frown "Seh, hola. ¿Te vas a quedar ahí paradote o qué?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:390
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d880744d:

    # ks sigh "Hey, girls. It was rough for you too, huh?"
    ks sigh "Hola, chicas. Ustedes también lo tuvieron difícil, ¿eh?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:394
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b1d94ef0:

    # s smirk_right "Speak for yourself." with dissolve
    s smirk_right "Habla por ti." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:397
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f12233d0:

    # "I let out a little groan, and it feels like Nozomi and even Hiroko joined in." with dissolve
    "Suelto un leve gruñido, y parece que Nozomi e incluso Hiroko se me unieron." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:398
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2da01aa4:

    # "Honestly, I could really use a break from all this pressure, and I have to wonder if my new associates feel the same way."
    "Honestamente, me vendría muy bien un descanso de toda esta presión, y me pregunto si mis asociadas sienten lo mismo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:402
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a0a7bc11:

    # ks neutral "Well... a-anyway, I thought maybe we could get back to planning for the culture fest? You know, now that we're done with that?" with dissolve
    ks neutral "Pues... e-en fin, ¿pensé que tal vez podríamos regresar a planear lo del festival cultural? Ya saben, ¿ahora que ya hemos terminado con eso?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:405
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b9b21cd7:

    # s uniform_folded frown_right "Oh, you three are most certainly not \"done with that\"." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded frown_right "Oh, los tres ciertamente no han \"terminado con eso\"." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:406
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2030534e:

    # h angry "'Sides, we said we'd get back on that shit tomorrow. What's the rush?" with dissolve
    h angry "Además quedamos en que seguiríamos con esa mierda mañana. ¿Por qué la prisa?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:402
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9c290308:

    # ks confused "W-well, the sooner the better, right? We can get our routine down and then we'll have time to figure these exams out after."
    ks confused "B-bueno, entre más pronto, mejor, ¿no? Podemos organizar la rutina y ya tendremos tiempo para descifrar estos exámenes después."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:408
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c141a6d6:

    # h uniform_armup irritated vein "Uhh, no? All those exams gave me a fuckin' headache. I'm gonna go home and crash." with dissolve
    h uniform_armup irritated vein "Eeh, ¿no? Todos esos exámenes me dieron una jaqueca del carajo. Voy a irme a casa y a dormir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:409
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_25098e05:

    # s sleeptalk "Besides, the school is essentially closed for the day but for our exams. The classrooms will be off limits for your activities." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Además, la escuela estará esencialmente cerrada el resto del día, salvo para los exámenes. Los salones de clase no estarán a su disposición para sus actividades." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:410
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ba5b931e:

    # n sad "Ahh, m-maybe that's not entirely true..." with dissolve
    n sad "Aah, t-tal vez eso no sea del todo cierto..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:412
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5749a846:

    # s concerned_right "Hmm?" with dissolve
    s concerned_right "¿Mmm?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:414
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ece168d4:

    # "Nozomi gently clears her throat before going on to explain herself." with dissolve
    "Nozomi se aclara gentilmente la garganta antes de explicarse." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:415
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_93a8cf28:

    # n "I-I mean, I could ask Ms. Chiba for the key. I'm the president of the literature club after all, and we get along pretty well."
    n "B-bueno, podría pedirle la llave a la profesora Chiba. Soy la presidenta del club de literatura, después de todo, y nos llevamos bastante bien."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:416
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_edcc5315:

    # n sad_side "So she'd probably allow it if I asked?" with dissolve
    n sad_side "Así que tal vez lo permita si le pregunto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:416
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7c052bc6:

    # h irritated vein "Are you {nw}" with dissolve
    h irritated vein "¿Hablas en {nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:419
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a9d0ca53:

    # extend "SERIOUS, lady?" with vpunch
    extend "SERIO, señorita?" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:420
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_28ed9d27:

    # "It's not often I see Hiroko shout at Nozomi like that."
    "No todos los días veo a Hiroko gritarle así a Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:421
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_74f2d68f:

    # n sad_closed "I-it was just an idea..." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "S-solo era una idea..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:422
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fc948a3f:

    # "But Nozomi has a point. Not to mention seeing Hiroko appear to be at the height of her irritability is only serving to redouble my motivation."
    "Pero Nozomi tiene razón. Sin mencionar que ver a Hiroko aparentemente en la cumbre de su irritabilidad solo aumenta mi motivación."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:423
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ddbdaefd:

    # "This would be the PERFECT time to try using the penlight on Hiroko as a test of its limits."
    "Este sería el momento PERFECTO para intentar usar la linterna en Hiroko y probar sus límites."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:427
