    # "Yep. Really going to enjoy dropping you in a few minutes, Hiroko..."
    "Sip. De veras voy a disfrutar hacerte caer en unos minutos, Hiroko..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:493
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_41d3a0db:

    # ks "Whatever. So are you ready to audition now? Gonna put on a good show for me?" with dissolve
    ks "Como sea. ¿Ya estás lista para tu audición? ¿Vas a darme un buen espectáculo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:495
