    n angry "¡Ya basta los dos! ¡Dejen de pelearse!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:500
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cc789683:

    # n "Ms. Chiba gave me special permission for us to be here, so don't you DARE embarrass me." with dissolve
    n "La profesora Chiba me dio permiso especial de estar aquí, así que no se ATREVAN a avergonzarme." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:501
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_38e4e6d1:

    # "Okay. I was trying to rile up Hiroko on purpose, but if Nozomi's this pissed as well then maybe I do need to cool it."
    "Está bien. Intentaba sacar un poco de quicio a Hiroko apropósito, pero si Nozomi está molesta también, tal vez sí deba calmarme."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:502
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d8241238:

    # ks sigh "Alright, fine. Let's just do what we came here to do."
    ks sigh "De acuerdo, bien. Solo hagamos lo que vinimos a hacer."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:503
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b1efd5f6:

    # h neutral "H'yeah, get it over with so we can go home." with dissolve
    h neutral "Seh, termina ya para que pueda irme a casa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:504
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b8abd5e6:

    # "Coming straight out of those exams probably put us all on edge enough as it is."
    "Venir directo de esos exámenes probablemente nos tiene a todos ya bastante estresados."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:507
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e209d5d1:

    # n smile_side "Okay, then~ So Hiroko, would you mind sitting down over here?" with dissolve
    n smile_side "Pues muy bien. Entonces, Hiroko, ¿podrías por favor sentarte aquí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:509
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_bc161f88:

    # "Still, agitated as she is, Nozomi's still plenty eager to get to business as she ushers Hiroko to one of the seats I set up." with dissolve
    "Sin embargo, por agitada que esté, Nozomi sigue bastante entusiasmada de continuar, y guía a Hiroko a uno de los asientos que preparé." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:515
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5481c440:

    # n smile "And Kyou?" with dissolve
    n smile "¿Y Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:516
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ac6adbc1:

