    ks neutral "¿Mm?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:519
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_74090602:

    # n "Would you like to give Hiroko a few pointers on how to be hypnotized?" with dissolve
    n "¿Quisieras darle a Hiroko algunas indicaciones de cómo ser hipnotizada?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:520
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_29678695:

    # n chuckle "Build a little rapport with your subject, perhaps?" with dissolve
    n chuckle "¿Darle algo de confianza a tu sujeto, quizás?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:521
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_561d94fe:

    # "She smiles pleasantly as she leaves Hiroko to stand beside me before whispering in my ear:"
    "Sonríe cordialmente, dejando a Hiroko junto a mí para luego susurrar en mi oído."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:522
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_112396ac:

    # n irritated "{size=16}Just don't be a jerk about it...{/size}" with dissolve
    n irritated "{size=16}Y no seas grosero...{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:524
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_adcdb3b8:

    # "Yeah, message received..." with dissolve
    "Seh, mensaje recibido..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:527
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1d1e93dc:

    # "I don't really want to tell Hiroko anything; just flash the penlight in her face and be done with it." with dissolve
    "No quiero decirle nada a Hiroko, a decir verdad; tan solo encenderle la linterna en la cara y listo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:528
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b2fa3b0a:

    # "But for the sake of appearances I'd best be professional about this, as I approach Hiroko with my best attempt at a smile."
    "Pero por las apariencias será mejor que actúe profesional, así que me acerco a Hiroko con mi mejor intento de sonrisa."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:528
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7fb86ac9:

    # ks smile "Alright, so getting hypnotized isn't that hard. All you need to do is relax, follow along to my words and just go with the flow."
    ks smile "Muy bien, pues ser hipnotizado no es tan difícil. Solo tienes que relajarte, seguir mis palabras y dejarte llevar."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:531
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_672e1b01:

    # ks "But most importantly, you need to WANT to be hypnotized, Hiroko. I can't do anything unless you allow me to, okay? Don't worry about a thing."
    ks "Pero lo más importante, tienes que QUERER ser hipnotizada, Hiroko. No puedo hacer nada a no ser que me dejes, ¿de acuerdo? No te preocupes por nada."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:533
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e9259962:

    # "Hiroko rolls her eyes and moodily folds her arms around her chest." with dissolve
    "Hiroko rueda los ojos y se cruza de brazos malhumorada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:533
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_019dac58:

    # h frown "H'yeah, the more you guys tell me not to worry the more sus I get."
    h frown "Seh, entre más me dicen que no me preocupe, más sospechoso me suena."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:536
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7462f5e1:

    # "I can tell from her body language that she's still tense, and she obviously doesn't trust me."
    "Puedo notar por su lenguaje corporal que sigue tensa, y obviamente no confía en mí."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:536
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d6d1c38c:

    # ns smile noglasses "I just want you to have some fun with this, Hiroko."
    ns smile noglasses "Solo quiero que te diviertas un poco, Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:538
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4b736b36:

    # "Normally that would be a problem..."
    "Normalmente eso sería un problema..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:539
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0651c3f7:

    # h sleeptalk "Whatever. I can handle Kyou for a couple minutes." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Como sea. Puedo aguantar a Kyou un par de minutos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:540
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f95a3e42:

    # h frown "Just don't try any creepy shit." with dissolve
    h frown "Solo no intentes mierdas raras." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:541
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2c187226:

    # "Normally a hypnotist would be nervous about hypnotizing someone like her. They'd probably send her back into the audience and find someone else..."
    "Normalmente un hipnotista estaría nervioso al hipnotizar a alguien así. Probablemente la regresaría a la audiencia y buscaría a alguien más..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:544
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cd62ccf0:

    # ks sigh "I'll do something simple and normal. Besides, Nozomi's going to be right here with us the whole time."
    ks sigh "Haré algo simple y normal. Además, Nozomi estará aquí con nosotros todo el tiempo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:545
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a9da48e7:

    # h angry "Alright, so get it done already!" with dissolve
    h angry "¡Muy bien, pues ya hazlo de una vez!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:559
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5dc0167a:

    # "But I'm more than happy for Hiroko to be difficult..."
    "Pero yo estoy más que feliz de que Hiroko sea difícil..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:560
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c75e3778:

    # ks neutral "Okay, then let's get started. Are you sitting comfortably?"
    ks neutral "De acuerdo, empecemos. ¿Estás cómoda?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:561
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_43c4ba99:

    # h frown "Yep..." with dissolve
    h frown "Sip..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:562
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_75b89a05:

    # ks neutral "Then I'd like you to take a nice deep breath and stare up at the light."
    ks neutral "Entonces quiero que respires profundo y mires la luz."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:567
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_95f5cedf:

    # ks "Taking a deep breath and as you exhale, notice how easy it becomes to focus on this light. On the pattern forming in your eyes."
    ks "Respira muy profundo, y al exhalar, nota lo fácil que es concentrarte en la luz. En el patrón que se forma en tus ojos."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:569
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c35cb046:

    # ks "Notice how effortless it becomes to let your limbs sink into the chair and relax, taking another deep breath..."
    ks "Nota lo sencillo que es dejar que tus brazos y piernas descansen en la silla y se relajen, respirando una vez más..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:572
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9fafddfe:

    # "Hiroko grumbles, but as I pass the light over her eyes a couple more times I can see those shoulders start to sag."
    "Hiroko refunfuña, pero tras pasar la luz por sus ojos un par de veces más, puedo ver que esos hombros comienzan a aflojarse."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:574
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4f5983e2:

    # ks "That's right. Very easy to focus. Very easy to relax..."
    ks "Eso es. Es muy fácil concentrarse. Muy fácil relajarse..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:576
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7ea5fdd3:

    # "And those eyes are just locked in position now. Waiting for every rhythmic pass of the light as she watches those patterns, fascinated in spite of herself."
    "Y esos ojos ahora están quietos en posición. Esperando cada rítmico pasar de la luz para observar esos patrones, fascinada lo quiera o no."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:578
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_23636671:

    # ks "There's no need to think about it at all. Just let yourself become more and more relaxed, just following the light. Letting everything else go, Hiroko."
    ks "No hay necesidad de pensarlo siquiera. Solo relájate más y más, siguiendo la luz. Dejando ir todo lo demás, Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:580
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fe2cde8a:

    # "All the while I notice Nozomi standing there from out of the corner of my eye, watching Hiroko intensely."
    "Todo mientras veo de soslayo a Nozomi, mirando a Hiroko con intensidad."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:582
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_53bab1dd:

    # ks "Breathing. Watching. Relaxing. Feeling yourself pulled deeper into the light. Letting it all go as you're pulled deeper now, Hiroko..."
    ks "Respira. Observa. Relájate. Siente cómo la luz te atrae más profundo. Dejando ir todo mientras te absorbe, Hiroko..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:589
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_11acc159:

    # "... And there it is. That distant look in her eyes as the light draws her in."
    "... Y ahí está. Esa mirada distante aparece en sus ojos ahora que la luz la está atrapando."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:590
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d2338a5e:

    # "It's just like the look Nozomi had."
    "Justo como la que tenía Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:592
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_15164ebd:

    # ks "{cps=20}That's right. Deeper and deeper, going all the way down as you... {/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"
    ks "{cps=20}Eso es. Más y más profundo, cayendo más y más y ahora... {/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:596
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4797c872:

    # extend "sleep, Hiroko."
    extend "duerme, Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:597
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e0f9cbf9:

    # "Snapping my fingers for effect, I allow the smile I've been restraining to spread across my lips as Hiroko drops hard in front of me."
    "Chasqueando mis dedos por efecto, dejo que la sonrisa que he estado conteniendo se expanda por mis labios, al ver a Hiroko caer frente a mí."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:599
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c2ec68b4:

    # ks smile "Dropping nice and deep, Hiroko. Deeper and deeper down into this nice, relaxing, dreamy state of hypnosis."
    ks smile "Cayendo muy profundo, Hiroko. Más y más profundo en este agradable, relajante y encantador estado de hipnosis."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:600
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_040cb7ca:

    # "I pause for a moment to look her over. She sure looks completely slumped in that chair now, and her breathing is slow and even. Very promising."
    "Hago una pausa para mirarla. Ahora sí que luce completamente arrumbada en esa silla, y su respiración es lenta y uniforme."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:601
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_925bd94b:

    # "But now the real fun is about to begin..."
    "Pero la verdadera diversión está por comenzar..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:602
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4b7fb2ba:

    # ks "That's very good, Hiroko. Now as you remain in this deep state of hypnosis that you are in now, I'd like you to lift your head back up..."
    ks "Muy bien, Hiroko. Ahora, aún en este profundo estado de hipnosis, quisiera que vuelvas a levantar la cabeza..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:603
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_47ae9c73:

    # ks "... That's right. And while still as deeply hypnotized as you are, I'd like you to open your eyes."
    ks "... Eso es. Y mientras sigues profundamente hipnotizada, quiero abras los ojos."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:620
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_acbc931b:

    # "The glassy-eyed stare is all the confirmation we need, as if we needed any more."
    "Esa mirada de ojos vidriosos es toda la confirmación que necesito, por si no tuviera suficiente."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:613
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5eaa12de:

    # "There's no way Hiroko could fake such a look, even if she knew how. This girl's deeply hypnotized, there's no doubt in my mind."
    "Hiroko no podría fingir una mirada así, incluso si la conociera. Esta chica está profundamente hipnotizada, no me queda duda."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:616
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b1980f5b:

    # "Whether or not she intended to be co-operative with me, or if she was nervous or calm about the prospect of me hypnotizing her, it doesn't seem to matter."
    "Así haya querido cooperar conmigo o no, o así estuviera nerviosa o calmada con la idea de que la hipnotizara, no parece importar."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:619
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4a12bac0:

    # "My penlight ensured she'd drop into trance for me no matter what."
    "Mi linterna aseguró que cayera en trance sin importar qué."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:620
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_56e9c137:

    # "It really DOES work on other people!"
    "¡O sea que SÍ funciona en otras personas!"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:629
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d5f76d8d:

    # ns concerned "{size=16}Um... Kyou?{/size}"
    ns concerned "{size=16}Em... ¿Kyou?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:623
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_12bc6dc8:

    # "Just then, Nozomi's soft whisper takes me out of my thoughts."
    "De pronto, el suave susurro de Nozomi me saca de mis pensamientos."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:624
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b0d409d2:

    # ks neutral "{size=16}What is it?{/size}"
    ks neutral "{size=16}¿Qué ocurre?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:633
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d60f2a44:

    # ns sleeptalk_concerned "{size=16}Could you have her close her eyes again, please?{/size}"
    ns sleeptalk_concerned "{size=16}¿Podrías hacerla cerrar los ojos otra vez, por favor?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:626
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ad3229b9:

    # "Oh, huh. I guess Hiroko DOES look a little creepy like that."
    "Oh, je. Creo que Hiroko SÍ da algo de miedo estando así."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:627
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c5f0bd84:

    # ks smile "Very good, Hiroko. You can close your eyes now."
    ks smile "Ya está bien, Hiroko. Puedes cerrar los ojos ahora."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:638
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e36c0c1a:

    # "Hiroko lets out a tiny sigh as her eyelids fall close and her head begins to droop downwards again."
    "Hiroko da un pequeño suspiro a la vez que sus párpados vuelven a descender y su cabeza cae hacia adelante una vez más."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:642
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_37b950a3:

    # n "{size=16}So what now, Kyou? You had something in mind, right?{/size}"
    n "{size=16}¿Y ahora qué, Kyou? ¿Tenías algo en mente?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:632
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_27594f28:

    # "Right. We didn't actually get a chance to discuss what exactly I'd do with Hiroko while she's tranced."
    "Cierto. Nunca tuvimos la oportunidad de discutir exactamente lo que haría con Hiroko mientras estuviera en trance."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:633
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_75ec382a:

    # "I also could've sworn I saw Nozomi tremble as she asked me. Is she excited about seeing Hiroko acting under a suggestion?"
    "Y podría jurar que vi a Nozomi temblar un poco al preguntarme. ¿Le emociona ver a Hiroko actuar bajo una sugestión?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:645
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_637fcbba:

    # ks "{size=16}Yeah, I thought about telling her her tongue's falling out of her mouth so she can't talk without it getting in the way.{/size}"
    ks "{size=16}Sí, se me ocurrió decirle que su lengua se le está cayendo de la boca y que no puede hablar sin que le estorbe.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:637
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4dc656b5:

    # "I'm about to turn my attentions back to Hiroko, only I catch Nozomi making a face at me." with dissolve
    "Estoy a punto de volver mi atención hacia Hiroko, solo para notar a Nozomi haciéndome una cara." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:638
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_77c44a43:

    # ks neutral "{size=16}What?{/size}"
    ks neutral "{size=16}¿Qué?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:639
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c1cbb038:

    # n irritated "{size=16}Do you really think she'll be comfortable with something like that?{/size}" with dissolve
    n irritated "{size=16}¿De verdad crees que estará cómoda con algo así?{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:640
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3da3a3f0:

    # "Honestly, Hiroko's comfort wasn't at the forefront of my mind, but I'd better not tell her that."
    "Honestamente, la comodidad de Hiroko no fue lo primero en lo que pensé, pero mejor no le digo eso."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:641
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7ee8cc05:

    # n pout_left "{size=16}I just think she could be really weirded out by that. Not to mention...{/size}" with dissolve
    n pout_left "{size=16}Creo que estaría muy extrañada con eso. Sin mencionar...{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:653
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_18f07726:

    # n sleeptalk_concerned "{size=16}Well, I can see her taking that phrasing badly.{/size}" with dissolve
    n sleeptalk_concerned "{size=16}Bueno, puedo imaginármela tomando mal esa oración.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:643
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_02b0b58c:

    # ks frown "{size=16}Really?{/size}"
    ks frown "{size=16}¿En serio?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:644
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_313623c5:

    # n frown "{size=16}Yes, really! She might think her tongue was getting in the way like you meant, or she might think her tongue was literally severed from her mouth!{/size}" with dissolve
    n frown "{size=16}¡Sí, en serio! ¡Puede que crea que su luenga le está estrobando como tenías pensado, o puede que crea que su lengua literalmente fue cortada!{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:645
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_edfe76b3:

    # n "{size=16}Do you want her screaming in pain, Kyou?{/size}"
    n "{size=16}¿Quieres verla gritar de dolor, Kyou?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:646
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ae9a6650:

    # ks frown "{size=16}... N-no?{/size}"
    ks frown "{size=16}... ¿N-no?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:647
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a656ad45:

    # n irritated "{size=16}I don't like how long you took to answer that.{/size}" with dissolve
    n irritated "{size=16}No me gusta que hayas tardado tanto en contestar eso.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:648
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fa2ae76d:

    # ks sigh "{size=16}Ugh, okay, nevermind. I'll think of something else...{/size}"
    ks sigh "{size=16}Ay, de acuerdo, olvídalo. Pensaré en otra cosa...{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:650
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9a49eaa9:

    # "She's right, though. I do need to be careful what I say to Hiroko while she's entranced if I want to avoid another zombie incident." with dissolve
    "Pero tiene razón. Debo tener cuidado con lo que le digo a Hiroko mientras está en trance si quiero evitar otro incidente zombi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:651
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c71058d5:

    # ks frown "{size=16}Okay, fine. I'll just tell her she can't speak for a while.{/size}"
    ks frown "{size=16}De acuerdo, bien. Solo voy a decirle que no puede hablar por un rato.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:653
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d6a7bd08:

    # "Nozomi folds her arms and sighs." with dissolve
    "Nozomi se cruza de brazos y suspira." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:664
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_dde60744:

    # n "{size=16}Somehow I'm not surprised you want to make her quiet...{/size}"
    n "{size=16}¿Por qué no me sorprende que la quieras callada?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:665
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_15eb0a7e:

    # n frown "{size=16}But okay. Just for a little while, and watch your wording.{/size}" with dissolve
    n frown "{size=16}Pero bien. Solo por un ratito, y cuida tus palabras.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:670
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_29c548ce:

    # "I nod, as I return to Hiroko's side and start to speak slowly and clearly."
    "Asintiendo, regreso al lado de Hiroko y comienzo a hablar lenta y claramente."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:686
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f062d245:

    # ks neutral "Okay Hiroko. I want you to imagine, in a few moments, not being able to speak."
    ks neutral "Muy bien, Hiroko. Quiero que imagines, en unos momentos, no ser capaz de hablar."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:673
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_95ada728:

    # ks "You'll still be able to move your lips and you'll always be able to breathe normally, but you won't be able to make a single sound come out of your mouth."
    ks "Aún podrás mover tus labios, y siempre podrás respirar con normalidad, pero no serás capaz de hacer que un solo sonido salga de tu boca."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:674
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f8eb9300:

    # ks "The more you try to speak, the more you'll find that you simply can't make a noise with your mouth. You'll only be able to move your lips. Do you understand?"
    ks "Entre más intentes hablar, más podrás ver que simplemente no puedes hacer ni un ruido con tu boca. Solo podrás mover tus labios. ¿Comprendes?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:675
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_46c324b7:

    # h sleeptalk "Yeah..." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Seh..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:678
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_30fd2e09:

    # "I give Nozomi a quick glance, in case she had something to say to me, but just gives me a little nod." with dissolve
    "Le doy a Nozomi una mirada rápida, en caso de que tenga algo que decirme, pero sencillamente asiente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:679
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1aa6b6c7:

    # "Seems she has no problems with my phrasing this time. So all that's left is to bring Hiroko out of trance and see how she does."
    "Parece que no tiene problemas con mis frases esta vez. Así que solo queda sacar a Hiroko del trance y ver cómo sale."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:694
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_440b6af5:

    # ks smile "Very good, Hiroko. Now when I count up to three you're going to awaken from this trance, feeling fully alert and awake in the reality I just described."
    ks smile "Muy bien, Hiroko. Ahora, cuando cuente a tres vas a despertar de este trance, sintiéndote completamente alerta y despierta en la realidad que acabo de describir."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:683
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_8ea95c79:

    # ks "Awakening in one, two..."
    ks "En uno, dos..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:684
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0fbe5069:

    # ks "Three, wide awake!"
    ks "¡Tres, despierta ahora!"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:703
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_dd3ad0ab:

    # "Hiroko's eyelids lazily pull back for a moment before she starts to sit up straight in front of us."
    "Los ojos de Hiroko se levantan vagamente y ella comienza a herguirse en su silla frente a nosotros."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:690
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_8005755b:

    # h surprised "..." with dissolve
    h surprised "..." with dissolve

