    n sad_closed "Para que la hipnosis funcione, siempre debe haber completa cooperación de la persona hipnotizada. Es un proceso colaborativo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:890
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cbc37a7d:

    # "But if we want to continue our experiments then what choice do we have but to keep the secrets of my penlight to ourselves?"
