translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e0c13c3a:

    # ks "And why is that, Sayori? Because I hypnotized you into going against your very nature?"
    ks "¿Y a qué se debe eso, Sayori? ¿Es porque te hipnoticé para actuar en contra de tu propia naturaleza?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1227
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c08b0f11:

    # "I watch as she starts to weep in frustration, even going so far as to violently slap her own thigh to futilely stir her unresponsive limbs back into motion." with dissolve
    "Veo cómo empieza a sollozar de frustración, la cual es tanta que golpea violentamente su propio muslo en un fútil intento de hacer reaccionar sus extremidades." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1229
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_cb3c8e74:

    # ks "I mean seriously. Why would a clever girl like you think I've been controlling your mind with hypnosis? That's what you've been implying all this time, right?"
    ks "En serio. ¿Por qué una chica lista como tú pensaría que he estado controlando su mente con hipnosis? Eso es lo que has estado insinuando todo este tiempo, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1230
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d45bde0d:

    # s "{cps=20}B-but your words... th-the light, it's the only logical explanation-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"
    s "{cps=20}P-pero tus palabras... l-la luz. Es la única explicación lógica-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1231
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9a772d0f:

    # ks angry "STOP lying to yourself!"
    ks angry "¡DEJA de mentirte!"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1232
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5ca2b1e1:

    # s "H-hrrrrgh!"
    s "¡G-grrrr!"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1233
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_1503e340:

    # ks frown "You know I've never tricked you. I've never tried to lead you astray. There's not a single thing I've done with you under hypnosis that you didn't agree to."
    ks frown "Sabes que nunca te engañé. Nunca he intentado llevarte por mal camino. No hay una sola cosa que haya hecho contigo bajo hipnosis que no hayas aprobado."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1237
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_750bd718:

    # s "Kyou... p-please, I..."
    s "Kyou... p-por favor, yo..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1238
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5af37de8:

    # ks "So what's really happening, Sayori? What's the logical explanation for this?"
    ks "Entonces, ¿qué ocurre en realidad, Sayori? ¿Cuál es la explicación lógica de todo esto?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1239
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_361d664b:

    # s "Haaah... b-because... I..."
    s "Haaah... e-es... porque yo..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1241
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7fa59a7a:

    # ks angry "Come on! Why are you like this?"
    ks angry "¡Vamos! ¿Por qué estás así?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1243
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_908cac13:

    # s blush "I-I..." with dissolve
    s blush "P-por..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1244
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_932dc592:

    # s "... Because I desire to be hypnotized... I-I wish for your hypnosis to affect me... is that what you want me to admit?"
    s "... Porque deseo ser hipnotizada... A-anhelo que tu hipnosis me afecte... ¿es eso lo que quieres que admita? "

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1246
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d36b6184:

    # s "Th-that this-s... desire has dominated my every waking thought, pushing... p-pushing everything else aside as I yearn for its... utterly... w-wonderful embrace?"
    s "¿Qu-que este-e... deseo ha dominado mis pensamientos, haciendo... ha-haciendo todo lo demás a un lado al añorar esa calidez tan... plenamente... m-maravillosa?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1250
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_fb3f422f:

    # s "Damn... d-damn you."
    s "Ma-... m-maldito seas."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1251
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c2e163f6:

    # "Shit... As her arms cease to strain against the floor and she breaks down sobbing I realize I've gone too far trying to prove my point."
    "Mierda... Al ver que sus brazos cesan de forcejear contra el suelo y ella rompe en lágrimas, me doy cuenta de que fui muy lejos tratando de probar mi punto."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1252
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5f8b785c:

    # "So I take a deep breath and try to clear my head while she's surely lost hers."
    "Así que respiro hondo e intento aclarar mi cabeza mientras que ella claramente ha perdido la suya."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1253
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_71fa9800:

    # "This isn't the time to be angry. I need her to confront the truth at last, but I also need to be gentle."
    "Este no es momento para enojarme. Necesito que encare finalmente la verdad, pero también debo ser gentil."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1254
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8b54c3ea:

    # ks sigh "H-hey, I'm sorry. I know you're scared but you get it, don't you?"
    ks sigh "O-oye, lo siento. Sé que tienes miedo, pero lo entiendes, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1255
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8598563d:

    # ks "It's not me you're afraid of. Not really anyway."
    ks "No soy yo a quien temes. No realmente."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1259
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_899d171c:

    # ks neutral "You're scared of yourself... aren't you." with dissolve
    ks neutral "Tienes miedo de ti misma... ¿no es así?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1260
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_bdf27196:

    # "Sayori lets out a shuddered sigh as she nods resignedly."
    "Sayori suelta un fatigado suspiro y asiente con resignación."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1262
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b90795f0:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "F-from the morning that followed our first hypnosis session... I have felt as though I were no longer in control of myself." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "D-desde la mañana posterior a nuestra primera sesión de hipnosis... me he sentido como si ya no tuviera control de mí misma." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1263
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_95fc8945:

    # s "The very idea that I would resolutely submit to these instructions of yours seemed like the purest fantasy."
    s "La idea de que me sometiera tan resueltamente a tus instrucciones parecía la más pura fantasía."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1265
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a3fa3145:

    # s "But you... ugh... y-you are right." with dissolve
    s "Pero... aj... t-tienes razón." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1266
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d8a3d773:

    # s "In trying to rationalize what had happened to me I merely retreated into a deeper fantasy."
    s "Intenté racionalizar lo que me había pasado y tan solo me refugié en una fantasía más profunda."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1267
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_21997534:

    # s "One that placed you as a villain, and I a helpless victim of your sinister machinations."
    s "Una que te pintó a ti como el villano, y a mí como la víctima indefensa de tus perversas maquinaciones."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1271
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5037675a:

    # s alert_concerned_right "I... know that there is a part of me that wishes to be led into a state of mental oblivion, and embrace it fully." with dissolve
    s alert_concerned_right "Sé... que hay una parte de mí que desea ser dirigida al estado mental de la inconsciencia, y aferrarme a él." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1272
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_10252e09:

    # s "And I cannot deny the hypnotic experience is... w-wonderously pleasurable. An utterly wonderful sensation I had not imagined could be possible."
    s "Y no puedo negar que la experiencia hipnótica es... m-maravillosamente placentera. Una sensación plenamente maravillosa que nunca imagine posible."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1274
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5f71e43f:

    # s alert_sleeptalk_concerned "You did not place such a desire in me, Kyou. You are no villain in this story. Your foray into hypnosis merely awakened it within me." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk_concerned "Tú no pusiste tal deseo en mí, Kyou. No eres el villano de esta historia. Tu incursión en la hipnosis meramente lo hizo despertar en mi interior." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1275
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_09df5f56:

    # s "That is the truth. And yet it is this truth which frightens me beyond all reason."
    s "Esa es la verdad. Y sin embargo es esta la verdad que me aterra más allá de la razón."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1277
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c3ebcef0:

    # s alert_cry "... F-f-forgive me." with dissolve
    s alert_cry "... R-r-ruego tu perdón." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1278
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_73d20585:

    # "I sigh gently as I look down on her weeping form."
    "Suspiro suavemente, viéndola sollozar en el suelo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1282
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_402820b7:

    # "Sayori's a proud woman. Admitting something like this has gotta be tough on her."
    "Sayori es una mujer orgullosa. Admitir algo así debe ser duro para ella."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1283
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2e978a20:

    # "But at least now we can find a way to move on, and in a way that'll suit both our needs."
    "Pero al menos ahora podemos hallar una manera de seguir adelante, y de una forma que satisfaga las necesidades de ambos."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1286
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_df7c841b:

    # ks sigh "It's alright. I mean, you've been stressing yourself for all this time that you don't know any other way to be, right?"
    ks sigh "Descuida. Digo, llevas tanto tiempo sometiéndote al estrés que ya no sabes cómo vivir de otra forma, ¿no es cierto?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1289
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_05171096:

    # s alert_concerned "Haah... r-right." with dissolve
    s alert_concerned "Haah... c-cierto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1290
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d7383956:

    # ks neutral "But if your subconcious has shown you anything it's that you need this. Sleeping it off every night is helping, but you're completely burnt out."
    ks neutral "Pero si algo ha mostrado tu subconsciente es que necesitas esto. Dormir bien cada noche ayuda, pero estás completamente agotada."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1291
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ed102da6:

    # ks "You need more. You need some time to truly relax and free your mind, Sayori. I think you need to let everything go."
    ks "Necesitas más. Necesitas tiempo para relajarte y liberar tu mente, Sayori. Creo que necesitas dejar ir todo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1293
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_59772b34:

    # s alert_surprised_right "You are asking me to... g-give up? On everything?" with dissolve
    s alert_surprised_right "¿Me pides que... r-renuncie? ¿A todo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1294
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8b30a14c:

    # ks "Yeah. I'm not saying forever, just for as long as you need until all that pent-up stress is gone. Until you can be happy with yourself again."
    ks "Sí. No digo que para siempre, solo el tiempo que necesites para que todo ese estrés acumulado se vaya. Hasta que puedas ser feliz contigo misma."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1295
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_fb15c289:

    # s alert_concerned "..."
    s alert_concerned "..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1296
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7f1f433a:

    # ks "Do you trust yourself, Sayori? Do you trust that part of you that \"wishes to be led\"?"
    ks "¿Confías en ti, Sayori? ¿Confías en esa parte de ti que \"desea ser dirigida\"?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1298
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_df5b8c4f:

    # s alert_concerned_right "I... y-yes." with dissolve
    s alert_concerned_right "Eh... s-sí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1299
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_16ba0b42:

    # ks "And do you trust me?"
    ks "¿Y confías en mí?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1300
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e1554201:

    # s "..."
    s "..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1302
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0677666b:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "... Yes." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "... Sí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1303
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0715f28a:

    # "After all the times she's accepted me leading her with hypnosis, I think it's logical of her to accept that she does trust me all things considered."
    "Después de aceptar tantas veces que la dirigiera con hipnosis, creo que es lógico aceptar que confía en mí a pesar de todo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1304
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_424922fe:

    # ks "Alright. So like I showed you last week, the fact you're under a hypnotic suggestion right now means you're currently under a light hypnotic trance."
    ks "Muy bien. Pues como te demostré la semana pasada, el hecho de que estés bajo una sugestión hipnótica ahora mismo significa que estás en un ligero trance hipnótico."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1305
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_12caf5d7:

    # ks "So I want to take you all the way back into trance, expel all that stress weighing on you and get you in a place where you can feel safe about letting your hair down, okay?"
    ks "Así que solo debo llevarte más profundo, expulsar todo el estrés que cargas y conducirte a un lugar donde puedas sentirte segura de dejarte llevar."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1307
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_d855f422:

    # "I can hear her exhale sharply as I suggest taking her deeper. I can practically feel the desire coming off of her." with dissolve
    "La escucho exhalar agudamente ante la idea de ir más profundo. Puedo prácticamente sentir el deseo emanando de ella." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1309
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_19c5ffdb:

    # s alert_sleep "Okay." with dissolve
    s alert_sleep "De acuerdo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1311
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4f27e72c:

    # ks "And to do that, I want to try something. When I tell you to, I want you to give something up. Something that's been weighing down on you." with dissolve
    ks "Y para eso, quiero intentar algo. Cuando te diga, quiero que renuncies a algo. Algo de lo que te ha estado pesando." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1312
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_38f999ff:

    # ks "With each thing you let go you may find yourself becoming more relaxed, and your mind more empty until you can drop back into that wonderful state of full hypnosis again."
    ks "Con cada cosa que dejes ir te sentirás más relajada, y tu mente estará más vacía hasta que caigas de vuelta en ese maravilloso estado de hipnosis."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1313
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e53849e1:

    # ks "Are you with me so far?"
    ks "¿Todo claro hasta ahora?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1315
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f79c6e08:

    # "Sayori gives me a little nod. She must be tired trying to hold herself up with just her hands, feeling the tension in those shoulders."
    "Sayori asiente levemente. Debe estar cansada de intentar sostenerse con solo sus manos, sintiendo la tensión en esos hombros."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1316
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0583a07c:

    # "Surely with her established desire, and her growing exhaustion, I won't need my penlight at all to make her drop tonight."
    "Estoy seguro de que, con su establecido deseo, y su creciente cansancio, no necesitaré mi linterna para hacerla caer esta noche."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1317
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_85768fe0:

    # ks "Good. So let's start with something simple: I want you to give up trying to manage my hypnosis show and assist me on stage instead."
    ks "Bien. Comencemos con algo simple: Quiero que renuncies a intentar gestionar mi espectáculo de hipnosis y simplemente seas mi asistente."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1318
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9119376e:

    # ks "I'll be the one to set the agenda and all you'll have to do is follow my directions. You won't have to worry about a thing, alright?"
    ks "Seré yo quien establezca el programa y tú solo tendrás que seguir mi dirección. No tendrás que preocuparte por nada, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1319
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_70bad49c:

    # s "... Alright. I shall allow this."
    s "... De acuerdo. Lo permitiré."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1320
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_171a207a:

    # ks "Good. It's a small thing, but even now you might find a little weight lifted from your mind. Feels good not having to think about it anymore, right?"
    ks "Bien. Es algo pequeño, pero incluso ahora notarás algo de peso quitándose de tu mente. Se siente bien ya no tener que pensar en eso, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1321
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_dfe8fa64:

    # "Sayori frowns slightly as I see her turning the concept over in her head."
    "Sayori frunce ligeramente el ceño. Puedo ver que le da vueltas al concepto en su cabeza."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1322
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2f5bfe65:

    # "She knows what it is I'm trying to do, but I have a feeling that's only going to excite her now."
    "Sabe qué es lo que intento hacer, pero tengo el presentimiento de que no hará más que emocionarla."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1324
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0638439d:

    # s "I... suppose." with dissolve
    s "S-... supongo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1325
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8f9064dc:

    # "Although what I'm going to tell her next is really going to test how committed she is to our new understanding."
    "Aunque lo que voy a decirle después pondrá realmente a prueba su compromiso con nuestro nuevo entendimiento."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1326
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_af67ce02:

    # ks "Now I want you to give up your study club."
    ks "Ahora quiero que renuncies a tu club de estudio."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1328
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b9407a96:

    # s alert_panicked_right "Wh-what? Y-you cannot possibly suggest that in all seriousness!" with dissolve
    s alert_panicked_right "¿Qu-qué? ¡N-no puedes estar hablando en serio!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1329
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8053319e:

    # s "{cps=20}I... I have an obligation to-{/cps}{w=0.8}{nw}"
    s "{cps=20}Tengo... Tengo una obligación para con-{/cps}{w=0.8}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1330
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_71191a9b:

    # ks neutral "Hey, remember what I said. And what you said just now."
    ks neutral "Oye, recuerda lo que dije. Y lo que tú misma dijiste."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1332
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e2edeaac:

    # s alert_surprised "O... of course. I trust you." with dissolve
    s alert_surprised "P-... por supuesto. Confío en ti." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1334
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2a592b8d:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "... I shall inform my club associates that I will be temporarily excusing myself from club duties... for personal reasons." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "... Les informaré a mis asociados del club que me ausentaré temporalmente a las actividades... por motivos personales." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1335
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7f875cc1:

    # ks "Feeling a little lighter still. Head a little clearer, perhaps a little blanker, now you've given up another responsibility."
    ks "Y te sientes un poco más ligera. Tu cabeza está un poco más clara, quizás casi en blanco, ahora que renunciaste a otra responsabilidad."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1337
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_fd019ff5:

    # "Sayori exhales quietly. She certainly seems a lot calmer for following along with what I'm doing here. Her eyes a little unfocused..." with dissolve
    "Sayori exhala suavemente. Ciertamente luce mucho más calmada gracias a seguirme la corriente. Sus ojos comienzan a desenfocarse..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1338
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a6ea22cf:

    # "She really is super suggestible, even in this light trance brought on by her still-active trigger."
    "Sí que es supersugestionable, incluso en este trance leve brindado por su aún activa ancla hipnótica."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1339
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_6e7eef57:

    # "Time to take her all the way down."
    "Hora de llevarla hasta el fondo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1340
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_84fd5f74:

    # ks "And the more you give up, the easier it becomes, Sayori. And the easier it becomes the lighter your head will feel. The blanker you'll be."
    ks "Y con cada cosa a la que renuncias, se vuelve más fácil, Sayori. Y entre más fácil se vuelve, más ligera se siente tu cabeza, y más en blanco estarás."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1341
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_738c91e4:

    # ks "So let's just go ahead and quit going to cram school now."
    ks "Así que ahora deja de ir a los cursos nocturnos."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1343
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_83c176ce:

    # s alert_panicked_right "I-I..." with dissolve
    s alert_panicked_right "E-eh..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1345
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0deed4ff:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "... will take a temporary leave of absence. My parents will understand, I think." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "... cesaré de asistir temporalmente. Mis padres comprenderán, creo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1346
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_12b09ca3:

    # ks frown "In fact, just give up studying entirely."
    ks frown "De hecho, renuncia a toda clase de estudio."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1348
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_780c1b19:

    # s alert_sleepy "I... will cease any attempt to st-... study..." with dissolve
    s alert_sleepy "Voy... a cesar cualquier intento de es-... estudio..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1349
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ca922434:

    # ks "And give up any notion of responsibility in this moment."
    ks "Y renuncia a cualquier noción de responsabilidad en este momento."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1352
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0c84980a:

    # s noblush "U... u-uh..." with dissolve
    s noblush "Eh... e-eh..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1353
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e49020d7:

    # ks "Head becoming emptier, Sayori. More and more blank as you shed every responsibility you have..."
    ks "Tu cabeza se vacía, Sayori. Más y más en blanco, dejando que toda responsabilidad se esfume..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1354
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_50fcf4b1:

    # s "Eh... e-every..."
    s "T-... t-toda..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1358
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4ccc0c7c:

    # ks "And sleep. Head completely empty, all responsibility gone. Just sinking deep into trance now, Sayori. So very deep." with dissolve
    ks "Y duerme. Mente completamente en blanco, sin ninguna responsabilidad. Sumérgete más profundo en trance, Sayori. Muy, muy profundo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1359
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7ba4658e:

    # "As I snap my fingers to compel her, Sayori's head drops like a lead weight and I'm quick to guide her down to lie comfortably on my living room floor."
    "Chasqueando mis dedos con imponencia, la cabeza de Sayori cae como plomo y yo rápidamente la guío y la poso cómodamente en el suelo de mi sala."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1360
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a75aa8ee:

    # ks neutral "Sleep. Deep asleep now."
    ks neutral "Duerme. Profundamente dormida."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1361
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_419f1c16:

    # "Her body comes to a complete rest on the ground, and I go to sit down beside her."
    "Su cuerpo descansa por completo en el suelo, y yo me siento junto a ella."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1362
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_65721101:

    # "She already looks so peaceful there on the floor. Her mouth hanging slightly agape as she lets out a quiet, slow breath that almost sounds to me like a moan."
    "Ya luce tan pacífica en el piso. Su boca está ligeramente abierta y ella libera un suave y lento suspiro que casi suena como un gemido."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1363
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_884b8bfc:

    # "It's a world apart from the stressed-out brainiac furiously arguing with me just a few minutes ago."
    "No podría estar más alejada de la estresada y barbáricamente furiosa discusión que estaba teniendo conmigo hace solo unos minutos."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1364
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_6b4a42cb:

    # ks "So deep asleep. Feeling yourself going even deeper. Allowing all your thoughts, your cares, your worries... all of them to fade away."
    ks "Muy profundamente dormida. Dejando que todos tus pensamientos, tus angustias, tus preocupaciones... que todo se desvanezca."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1367
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_48987d22:

    # ks "Feeling every ounce of stress effortlessly drain from the top of your head, all the way down to the tips of your toes. Completely leaving your body now."
    ks "Sintiendo cada gramo de estrés sencillamente drenándose desde tu cabeza hasta los dedos de tus pies. Abandonando completamente tu cuerpo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1368
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7cd9536e:

    # ks "Because this is what you want, Sayori. You want your mind to become totally blank, free of any and all concerns."
    ks "Porque esto es lo que quieres, Sayori. Quieres que tu mente esté totalmente en blanco, libre de toda preocupación."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1369
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9402dde0:

    # "And then it hits me."
    "Y entonces me doy cuenta."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1370
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_3bd277c7:

    # ks "... Like a doll."
    ks "... Como una muñeca."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1371
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_50bfa5d6:

    # "Sayori's already very familiar with dolls. What girl isn't?"
    "Sayori ya está muy familiarizada con las muñecas. ¿Qué chica no lo está?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1372
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b846abac:

    # ks "Dolls have no thoughts or concerns... do they, Sayori?"
    ks "Las muñecas no tienen pensamientos ni preocupaciones... ¿o sí, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1373
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4d1c9665:

    # s "{size=16}... No.{/size}"
    s "{size=16}... No.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1374
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_602b98ae:

    # "But moreso, she already had some interest in playing along with the concept of becoming a doll."
    "Y no solo eso, sino que también tenía ya cierto interés en explorar el concepto de convertirse en muñeca."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1375
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f5bda831:

    # ks "No thoughts. No concerns. All they do is lie there and look cute, waiting to be played with... right?"
    ks "Sin pensamientos. Sin preocupaciones. Lo único que hacen es estar ahí y verse bonitas, anhelando que jueguen con ellas... ¿cierto?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1376
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_750f78e2:

    # s "{size=16}... Uh-huh.{/size}"
    s "{size=16}... Aja.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1377
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_f8490ac5:

    # "She may have shut me down before, but she was nervous back then. Nervous about being hypnotized. Nervous about me."
    "Me habrá rechazado antes, pero estaba nerviosa entonces. Nerviosa de ser hipnotizada. Nerviosa por mí."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1378
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_63302182:

    # "But after everything that's happened between us... surely the time is right to suggest it again."
    "Pero luego de todo lo que ha pasado entre nosotros... debe ser el momento adecuado para sugerirlo otra vez."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1379
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2ca3c1bd:

    # ks "So wouldn't it be wonderful if you could also become a doll, Sayori? For as long as you want?"
    ks "Entonces, ¿no sería maravilloso si tú pudieras ser una muñeca, Sayori? ¿Por tanto tiempo como quieras?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1380
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b1a3392b:

    # "It'd be just what she needs to experience a state of true carefree bliss."
    "Sería justo lo que necesita para experimentar un verdadero estado de despreocupada dicha."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1381
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_750f78e2_1:

    # s "{size=16}... Uh-huh.{/size}"
    s "{size=16}... Ajá.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1382
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_1b9d81a8:

    # "And a perfect way to indulge her professed love for being hypnotized."
    "Y la forma perfecta de consentir su declarado amor por ser hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1383
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_6898cc5d:

    # ks "Yes it would. A beautiful, mindless doll. So when I wake you in a few moments you are going to open your eyes and become the most beautiful, most perfect doll that you can be."
    ks "Claro que sí. Una hermosa muñeca sin mente. Así que, a las tres, abrirás los ojos y te convertirás en la más bella y perfecta muñeca que puedas ser."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1384
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_bf0deeeb:

    # ks "A most perfect, carefree doll in one two, and..."
    ks "Una perfecta y despreocupada muñeca en uno, dos, y..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1393
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c7269c21:

    # ks "Three, wide awake and..."
    ks "Tres, despierta y..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1388
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5b139a6d:

    # "I lean in to watch as Sayori's eyelids gently pull back and reveal a pair of glistening yet seemingly lifeless eyes."
    "Me acerco un poco para ver los párpados de Sayori alzarse, revelando un par de ojos relucientes, y sin embargo vacíos de vida."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1389
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e1554201_1:

    # s "..."
    s "..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1390
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b1fb7f8a:

    # "Those eyes seem to have nothing going on behind them. She could well still be in the deepest of hypnotic trances with that kind of expression."
    "No parece ocurrir nada detrás de esos ojos. Bien podría seguir en un trance hipnótico de lo más profundo con esa expresión."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1391
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8c439154:

    # ks "Sayori... can you hear me?"
    ks "Sayori... ¿puedes oírme?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1392
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_60ab3a3f:

    # "... There's nothing. I'm not even sure if she consciously heard me."
    "... Nada. Ni siquiera sé si me oyó conscientemente."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1393
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7746226d:

    # "Were the faintest rise and fall of her chest not betraying the fact she still breathes I'd have been convinced this truly were a life-sized doll laying before me."
    "De no delatar que aún respira el tenue subir y bajar de su pecho, estaría convencido de que esto que yace ante mí es realmente una muñeca sin vida."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1394
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_a1417f06:

    # "And I have to believe she's perfectly happy like this. Existing, in this moment, as much an unthinking object as one could possibly be."
    "Y he de creer que así es perfectamente feliz. Existiendo, en este momento, tan cercana a un objeto no pensante como se puede ser."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1395
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_919d34ce:

    # "But what to do with her? I could leave her like this, just letting her lie in this deep meditative state..."
    "Pero ¿qué hago con ella? Podría dejarla así, dejándola recostada en este profundo estado meditativo..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1396
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_78e796ac:

    # "Or maybe I could ... \"play\" with her? She IS a doll in her own mind, after all. She'd be expecting it."
    "¿O tal vez pueda... \"jugar\" con ella? En su mente ella ES una muñeca, después de todo. Es lo que esperaría."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1397
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_cfbea53d:

    # "I gotta be gentle, though. She looks so fragile lying like this."
    "Debo ser delicado. Luce tan frágil así."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1398
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_b063c0eb:

    # "So I'll just... carefully pick her up by the shoulders. Lift her slowly to have her sit upright on the floor in front of me."
    "Solo voy a... tomarla con cuidado de los hombros. La levantaré lentamente para sentarla en el suelo frente a mí."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1415
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7ff03ea2:

    # "As I sit her up, her head flops limply to the side. Like, wow, even while I'm disturbing her like this there isn't a resisting bone in her whole body." with dissolve
    "Ya sentada, su cabeza cae floja hacia un lado. O sea, vaya, incluso perturbándola así no hay ni rastro de resistencia en su cuerpo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1400
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c7d60ccc:

    # "I never suggested what kind of doll she might be, but as limp as she is she's basically a rag doll."
    "Nunca le dije qué clase de muñeca sería, pero así de floja, básicamente es una muñeca de trapo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1401
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_dbae1d11:

    # "How do I \"play\" with a doll like this? All I'm doing is holding her and getting her hair in my mouth."
    "¿Cómo se \"juega\" con una muñeca así? No hago más que sostenerla y -lograr que su cabello se me meta a la boca."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1402
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7a5e8dda:

    # "I'll just push that aside and... wow, that feels good to touch. Her hair is like silk."
    "Lo haré a un lado y... guau, se siente bien. Su cabello es como ceda."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1403
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c24c3d49:

    # "After arranging her hair to sit more behind her shoulders, I reach up and start to pet the top of her head while she lies still in my arms."
    "Tras acomodar su cabello detrás de sus hombros, llevo mi mano a la parte de arriba de su cabeza, sujetándola en mis brazos."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1404
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_480e81c8:

    # "... I should probably be more weirded out about this than I am, but... this feels nice. It's nice, seeing this vulnerable side to Sayori."
    "... Esto tal vez debería extrañarme más, pero... se siente bien. Es lindo ver este lado vulnerable de Sayori."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1405
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_65d3f8b6:

    # "She truly needed this. To be able to live in a moment she can feel completely free from all the stresses of the world."
    "Sí que necesitaba esto. Ser capaz de vivir un momento en el que pudiera sentirse completamente libre del estrés del mundo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1406
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_30cdd737:

    # "A moment where she can stop caring about anyone and anything else. A moment where she can let someone else do the caring."
    "Un momento en el que puedo dejar de preocuparse de nadie y de nada más. Un momento en el que puede dejar que alguien más cuide de todo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1409
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_3c54adb5:

    # "... You can let me care for you, Sayori."
    "... Puedes dejarme cuidar de ti, Sayori."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2022-05-30 11:34

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1363
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_6dc36a78:

    # "Her body comes to a complete rest on the ground as I watch."
    "Observo cómo su cuerpo descansa por completo en el suelo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1369
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9f475265:

    # "As I speak I go to sit down beside her and start gently massaging her shoulder."
    "Mientras hablo, me siento junto a ella y comienzo a masajear suavemente su hombro."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1371
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_6e292156:

    # "If there's a way to leave her even more deeply relaxed and content, I very much want her to achieve it."
    "Si hay alguna forma de hacerla sentirse más profundamente relajada y contenta, quiero conseguirla."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2022-06-21 22:31

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1312
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_41905002:

    # "Sayori exhales sharply as I suggest taking her deeper. I can practically feel the desire coming off of her." with dissolve
    "Sayori exhala agudamente ante la idea de ir más profundo. Puedo prácticamente sentir el deseo emanando de ella." with dissolve
# TODO: Translation updated at 2022-10-14 11:46

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1851
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_644b66ea:

    # "The next couple days pass slowly, but uneventfully."
    "El próximo par de días transcurre lentamente, pero sin eventos."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1853
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_bbe6499e:

    # "After our little negotiation we mostly kept out of each other's way, turning our minds to the more pressing issue of our exams."
    "Tras nuestra pequeña negociación cada quien se fue por su lado, pasando nuestra atención al tema más demandante que son nuestros exámenes."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1854
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_32515059:

    # "At least, that's what I imagine those two were doing. As for me, I couldn't focus on them at all."
    "Al menos eso imagino que hicieron esas dos. En cuanto a mí, no me pude concentrar en ellos ni por un segundo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1855
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_be4f3195:

    # "And now here I am, hanging around the hallway having just finished those torturous mock exams."
    "Y ahora heme aquí, parado en el pasillo recién habiendo terminado esos tortuosos exámenes simulacro."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1856
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_499df5cc:

    # "How did I do? Well, let's just say it's good that those weren't the real college entrance exams because if they were I'd be lucky to be invited to study anywhere..."
    "¿Cómo me fue? Bueno, solo digamos que es un alivio que no fueran mis verdaderos exámenes de admisión. De serlo tendría suerte si me invitaran a estudiar a algún lado..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1894
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_6169b7c9:

    # "But... never mind that. I just spied Hiroko and her friends filing out of the classroom." with dissolve
    "Pero... olvidémonos de eso. Acabo de ver a Hiroko y sus amigas salir del salón." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1895
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_28bbd8c7:

    # h "Fuckin' glad that's over."
    h "La puta madre, cuánto me alegro de que haya terminado."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1896
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_d8bda8d3:

    # n "That... makes two of us, Hiroko."
    n "Ya... somos dos, Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1897
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_31eee434:

    # "Judging from those glum faces I guess those two didn't fare much better than me."
    "A juzgar por esos cabizbajos rostros, supongo que no les fue mucho mejor que a mí."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1901
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_3be9631e:

    # s uniform_handup concerned "Did you really find it so difficult?" with dissolve
    s uniform_handup concerned "¿En serio les pareció tan complicado?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1904
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_341f3fc8:

    # h "H'yeah, well it ain't like I had a chance anyway. That tourney took it all out of me." with dissolve
    h "Seh, bueno, de todos modos no tenía oportunidad. Ese torneo extrajo todo de mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1905
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_e3147577:

    # s neutral "That may be, but I do hope you have not simply given up. Even a sports-focused college will require you to demonstrate some academic ability." with dissolve
    s neutral "Puede ser, pero espero que no te hayas simplemente dado por vencida. Incluso una universidad enfocada en los deportes te exigirá mostrar habilidad académica." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1906
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_fe0b72d0:

    # h uniform_headhold2 irritated "Gawd, I know! Just cut me some slack, okay?" with dissolve
    h uniform_headhold2 irritated "¡Aj, ya sé! No tienes que regañarme." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1907
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_385f16d3:

    # h frown_side "I got another shot at it, an' next time I won't miss, got it?" with dissolve
    h frown_side "Tengo otra oportunidad y la próxima no fallaré, ¿quedó claro?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1908
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_fd888e31:

    # s smile "Understood. But I wonder what your excuse is, Miss Akemi?" with dissolve
    s smile "Comprendo. Pero me pregunto cuál es tu excusa, ¿señorita Akemi?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1910
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_1e38a213:

    # n "... I don't like that tone you're taking with me." with dissolve
    n "... No me gusta ese tono." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1911
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_f3b1b273:

    # s smirk "I do not like that you're evading the question." with dissolve
    s smirk "No me gusta esa evasión a la pregunta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1912
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_9669c34a:

    # n sad_closed "Just... I've had other things on my mind too, Sayori. That's all." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Es que... yo también he tenido otras cosas en mente, Sayori. Es todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1913
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_576f3dd0:

    # s uniform_folded sleeptalk "It is true that the scheduling was far from ideal but still, it is worrying that you seemed to have struggled so much with this." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded sleeptalk "Es cierto que la fecha estuvo lejos de ser la ideal, pero aun así es preocupante que les diera tantos problemas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1914
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_0b1b8781:

    # s concerned "I just want you both to know that you can ask for assistance any time. I want us all to graduate without regrets." with dissolve
    s concerned "Solo quiero que ambas sepan que pueden solicitar mi asesoría cuando quieran. Quiero que todos nos graduemos sin arrepentimientos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1917
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_051eba13:

    # h nervous_side "Thanks, sis. Maybe we'll take you up on that." with dissolve
    h nervous_side "Gracias, hermana. Lo tendremos en mente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1918
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a5eab165:

    # s neutral "Very well, then." with dissolve
    s neutral "Muy bien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1919
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_518257a3:

    # s neutral_right "Oh, and Koyama?" with dissolve
    s neutral_right "Oh, y, ¿Koyama?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1922
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_55055c6f:

    # ks surprised "Uh, y-yeah?" with dissolve
    ks surprised "Eh, ¿s-sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1923
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_dce4dc57:

    # "Ah, so they noticed me hanging around."
    "Oh, conque notaron que estaba aquí."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1924
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_b9ef8941:

    # s frown_right "I extend my offer to you as well, since from that look on your face you apparently need it as much as they do." with dissolve
    s frown_right "Extiendo a ti mi oferta también, ya que, por la mirada en tu rostro, parece que la necesitas tanto como ellas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1925
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_358db3ac:

    # ks sigh "Uh, yeah... thanks."
    ks sigh "Eh, sí... gracias."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1927
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_e9dd6621:

    # "Sayori lets out a sigh and shakes her head; her disappointment with all of us palpaple." with dissolve
    "Sayori deja salir un suspiro y sacude la cabeza; su decepción de todos nosotros es palpable." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1928
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_dd6e2e9e:

    # s uniform_handup neutral "And with that I shall take my leave. I need to review my own answers from the test." with dissolve
    s uniform_handup neutral "Y dicho eso, debo retirarme. Tengo que revisar mis respuestas del examen." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:1930
