    multi "{size=16}A... aaaah...{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2680
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_89253272:

    # "A single word is all it takes to dispel their frightened looks and drop them back into peaceful oblivion." with dissolve
    "Una sola palabra es todo lo que hace falta para disipar sus temerosas miradas y regresarlas a la pacífica inconsciencia." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2682
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_5dcb6c2f:

    # "They're safe again in their own minds but... shit, this could be bad for me."
    "Están a salvo de nuevo en sus propias mentes, pero... mierda, ¿esto podría darme problemas?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2683
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_7a9a1f64:

    # "I turn once again back to my computer to be greeted by my gleeful audience voicing appreciation for the chaos they just witnessed."
    "Regreso una vez más a mi computadora para ser recibido por mi alegre audiencia, expresando su apreciación por el caos que acaban de presenciar."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2686
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_562d6bb9:

    # "They're all cheering on the girls for their amazing performance and hailing me, \"MindCoder\", as a new legend in the hypnosis community."
    "Están aclamando a las chicas por su maravilloso desempeño y llamándome a mí, \"MindCoder\", una nueva leyenda de la comunidad de hipnosis."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2618
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_78e022d9:

    # ks casual surprised "O-okay, guys, glad you enjoyed the show. That's all we got time for so... see you."
    ks casual surprised "M-muy bien, chicos, me alegra que disfrutaran el espectáculo. Eso es todo lo que tenemos por hoy... nos vemos."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2689
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_70730940:

    # "And with a hurried click I end the stream and shut down the chatroom app. We're alone again."
    "Y con un clic apresurado, termino la transmisión y cierro la aplicación de chat. Ahora estamos solos."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2690
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_4479bd6d:

    # "Alone with these girls is what I need to be right now. Because I need to fix this with them somehow."
    "Estar solo con estas chicas es lo que ahora necesito. Pues tengo que arreglar esto de alguna forma."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2691
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_5d2f8d72:

    # "If I let them leave here knowing what I did, knowing I didn't stick to the script, knowing I fucking humiliated them in front of all those people..."
    "Si dejo que se vayan de aquí sabiendo lo que hice, sabiendo que no me apegué al guion, sabiendo la puta humillación que las hice pasar en frente de toda esa gente..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2692
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a68db953:

    # "But... okay, I can do this. Even after everything that happened, nothing jolted them out of the hypnotic daze I placed their minds in."
    "Pero... muy bien, puedo hacer esto. Incluso después de todo lo que pasó, nada las sacó del espacio hipnótico en el que puse sus mentes."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2693
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_9965ed8a:

    # "They'll still accept anything I tell them."
    "Aún aceptarán todo lo que les diga."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2626
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_4f5cbfe8:

    # ks casual neutral "You're... you're both doing so well, girls. Remaining so hypnotized. Remaining so easy to hypnotize..."
    ks casual neutral "Lo... lo están haciendo muy bien, chicas. Permaneciendo completamente hipnotizadas. Tan relajadas y tan fáciles de hipnotizar."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2695
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_1b209a14:

    # "So... I'll pick up the costume masks littering the floor."
    "Así que... recogeré las máscaras del suelo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2696
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_6c4a9d71:

    # ks "And now that you're back in this state of wonderful... r-relaxing hypnosis I want you to focus on my words once more."
    ks "Y ahora que están de vuelta en este estado de maravillosa y... r-relajante hipnosis, quiero que se concentren en mis palabras una vez más."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2697
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_b55cceba:

    # "I'll reattach them to their peaceful, sleeping faces."
    "Las recolocaré en sus pacíficos rostros durmientes."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2698
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_0edba1f4:

    # ks "Because you both need to forget everything that happened tonight. You never kissed each other, you never had any unusual, lustful thoughts about your friend..."
    ks "Porque ambas deben olvidar todo lo que pasó esta noche. Nunca se besaron, nunca pensaron nada inusual ni lujurioso de su amiga..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2699
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_21e094a2:

    # "That's right. I can make them do anything I want."
    "Es cierto. Puedo lograr que hagan lo que quiera."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2700
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a6b9b6b5:

    # ks "Your every memory of what occurred during our show will become so easy, so effortless to simply forget."
    ks "Les será muy fácil olvidar los recuerdos de lo que pasó durante nuestro acto."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2701
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_ebd5fe0d:

    # ks "So natural to simply seal away those memories in your minds where you will never be able to find them. Never be able to even think of finding them."
    ks "Muy natural el simplemente sellar esos recuerdos en sus mentes donde nunca podrán encontrarlos. Nunca podrán siquiera pensar en encontrarlos."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2702
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_39a3ff1d:

    # "So I'll make them forget. And they WILL forget."
    "Así que las haré olvidar. Y VAN a olvidar."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2703
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a6f39cfb:

    # ks "Instead, you will remember that I performed our hypnosis show exactly as I planned it. You both had a lovely time and have nothing to be concerned about. Understand?"
    ks "En vez de eso recordarán que hicimos nuestro acto de hipnosis tal como planeamos. Ambas se la pasaron genial y no tienen nada de qué preocuparse. ¿Comprenden?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2706
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_94eb954e_2:

    # multi "Yes..." with dissolve
    multi "Sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2709
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_72aace1f:

    # ks "That's good, girls... very good. Accepting everything you were told and waking up feeling refreshed and happy in three, two... one..." with dissolve
    ks "Bien, chicas... muy bien. Aceptando todo lo que les acabo de decir, despertarán frescas y contentas en tres, dos... uno..." with dissolve

