    # "Nor Nozomi's. Although I gotta admit..."
    "Ni tampoco los de Nozomi. Aunque he de admitir..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2730
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_caae1524:

    # ks "Y-yeah... See you tomorrow, girls."
    ks "S-sí... hasta mañana chicas."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2731
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_cb1fd852:

    # "It's still nice to see them like this, after all the years they coldly brushed me off."
    "Es lindo verlas así, después de tantos años de rechazarme."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2732
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_83d7371b:

    # h happy "Laters~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    h happy "'Ta luego. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2737
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_23b0cf2f:

    # "With that the girls head out, chattering excitedly among themselves about the night they've just had." with dissolve
    "Y con eso las chicas se retiran, conversando con emoción sobre la noche que acaban de tener." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2740
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_cb889ba9:

    # "And as I close the door to my house, I breathe a pained sigh."
    "Y al cerrar le puerta de mi casa, exhalo un suspiro con dolor."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2741
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_7d81b4f9:

    # "They really don't suspect a thing."
    "De verdad no sospechan nada."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2744
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_ca374d2b:

    # "I... think I'm going to get away with it. I explored the limits of my hypnotic abilities and learned that the only limit is my imagination."
    "Creo... que voy a salirme con la mía. Exploré los límites de mis habilidades hipnóticas y descubrí que el único límite es mi imaginación."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2745
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_ce1581e0:

    # "And that's of I'm afraid of."
    "Y eso es lo que me temo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2748
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_73c16e8f:

    # "The thoughts I had... the very idea that I could mold those girls into exactly who I want them to be... it's scary. And so very tempting."
    "Las cosas que se me vinieron a la mente... la idea de que podría moldear a estas chicas y hacerlas lo que yo quiera... es aterradora. Y tan tentadora."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2749
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_71ba20b1:

    # "I can't allow myself to use this penlight again... can I?"
    "No puedo permitirme volver a usar esta linterna... ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2751
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_515c25c4:

    # "They'll be confused tomorrow if I tell them my days as a hypnotist are over, but it'll be okay. They'll respect it."
    "Mañana estarán confundidas si les digo que mis días como hipnotista se acabaron, pero estarán bien. Lo respetarán."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2752
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_51db68e7:

    # "And I can go back to being just a regular high school student."
    "Y yo puedo regresar a ser un estudiante común y corriente."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2753
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_ae09fbfb:

    # "Everything's going to be fine..."
    "Todo estará bien..."
