    # "I see a frown form on Nozomi's face. Yeah, I know how she really feels about removing it."
    "Veo el ceño de Nozomi fruncirse. Sí, sé lo que piensa realmente sobre removerla."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:2593
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_ce52c6d3:

    # n "What just happened?! Kyou, w-what just happened to us?"
    n "¡¿Qué pasó?! Kyou, ¿qu-qué nos pasó?"
