# game/Kyou 10.rpy:501
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_33c02f32:

    # n chuckle "Build a little rapport with your hypnotee, perhaps?" with dissolve
    n chuckle "¿Darle algo de confianza a tu sujeto, quizás?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:713
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_11062ebc:

    # "As she looks me full in the eye, there's no ignoring the movement of her lips which slowly and deliberately mouth the word \"motherfucker\"." with dissolve
    "Mirándome directo a los ojos, es imposible ignorar el movimiento en sus labios que lenta y deliberadamente articulan la frase \"hijo de puta\"." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:739
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6467e073:

    # "Without warning, I let my hand drop loose and Hiroko's hand slams down towards the floor with it. And as her hand dropped, so did the rest of her."
    "Sin advertencia, aflojo mi brazo y la mano de Hiroko se va de golpe en dirección al suelo. Y al caer su mano, cae también el resto de ella."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:786
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6a88834c:

    # "I take one more quick glance behind me to make sure Nozomi's still distracted by her conversation with Ms. Chiba before I make my move."
    "Doy otro rápido vistazo hacia atrás para asegurarme de que Nozomi siga distraída en la conversación con la profesora Chiba antes de hacer mi jugada."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:789
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4bc7362e:

    # "Her back is still turned, her focus still on our English literature teacher, so with my heart in my mouth I lean in as close as I dare to Hiroko's slumped head..."
    "Sigue con la espalda hacia nosotros, su atención aún en nuestra profesora de literatura castellana."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:790
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_eb846ca7:

    # ks "{size=16}So now Hiroko, the next time you wake you will quickly realize that you enjoy being hypnotized.{/size}"
    ks "{size=16}Bien, Hiroko, cuando despiertes, rápidamente te darás cuenta de que disfrutas ser hipnotizada.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:791
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1d4ecad9:

    # "I calmly whisper a couple of quick phrases into her ear while I feel my blood pumping..."
    "Susurro calmadamente un par de rápidas frases en su oído mientras siento cómo mi corazón se acelera..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:791
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6013f5e9:

    # ks "{size=16}You enjoy being hypnotized. So it's only natural that you will want me to hypnotize you again.{/size}"
    ks "{size=16}Disfrutas ser hipnotizada. Así que es natural que quieras que te hipnotice otra vez.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:795
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_039edcaf:

    # "Two quick, yet potentially very powerful phrases. That's as much as I dare to try before I stand up straight and take another nervous glance behind me."
    "Dos rápidas, pero seguramente muy poderosas frases. Y eso es todo lo que me atrevo a intentar antes de erguirme y dar otro nervioso vistazo atrás de mí."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:804
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_66eb36dd_1:

    # t "You do seem to have a love for the unconventional, if your writing assignments are anything to go by."
    t " Vaya que tienes un amor por lo poco convencional, a juzgar por tus tareas de escritura."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:806
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_de0d4d99_1:

    # n "Ahahaha... t-thank you?"
    n "Ajajaja... ¿g-gracias?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:824
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a64387d1:

    # "Swallowing dryly, I anxiously nod my head."
    "Tragando saliva, asiento ansiosamente con la cabeza."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:825
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_88beddb0:

    # ks confused "{size=16}I... w-well yeah I was waiting for you, obviously.{/size}"
    ks confused "{size=16}Eh... b-bueno, sí, te estaba esperando, por supuesto.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:831
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_48d927a1:

    # "I probably could've played that a little cooler, but I think Nozomi's too flustered about Ms. Chiba to suspect anything from me."
    "Tal vez pude haber mostrado más serenidad, pero parece que los nervios por lo de la profesora Chiba la distraen de sospechar de mí."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:837
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c9d782ba:

    # "Nodding my head once more, I then lean towards Hiroko and lay a hand on her shoulder, just to make sure she knows I'm talking to her again after that commotion."
    "Asintiendo una vez más, me inclino hacia Hiroko y pongo una mano en su hombro, solo para asegurarme de que sepa que le estoy hablando a ella otra vez luego de la conmoción."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:842
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_16f6ec24:

    # ks "When you wake, you will find the suggestion I made to you about not being able to speak has now completely dropped from your mind."
    ks "Cuando despiertes, notarás que la sugestión que te di sobre no poder hablar habrá desaparecido de tu mente."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:843
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e0351f4d:

    # ks "So you'll be able to talk again without restrictions. Understand, Hiroko?"
    ks "Serás capaz de hablar de nuevo sin restricciones. ¿Comprendes, Hiroko?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:851
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e0a2afeb:

    # "I hope you do, Hiroko. I hope you understand I only want you to lose that one specific suggestion." with dissolve
    "Espero que sí, Hiroko. Espero que comprendas que solo quiero que pierdas esa sugestión en específico." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:852
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b7fdb4df:

    # ks "Good, Hiroko. That's very good."
    ks "Bien, Hiroko. Muy, muy bien."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:853
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a1f3804c:

    # "But if our private little experiment works out, you'll be helpless to resist following the one I made to you just now."
    "Pero si nuestro pequeño experimento privado funciona, no podrás resistir la otra que te acabo de dar."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:855
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6745b98c:

    # ks "Now then, becoming wide awake and fully refreshed on the count of three." with dissolve
    ks "Ahora despertarás sintiéndote fresca a la cuenta de tres." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:856
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_090b005a:

    # "If I'm right, you won't even realize you're following it and Nozomi won't suspect a thing."
    "Si estoy en lo correcto, ni siquiera te darás cuenta de que la estás siguiendo y Nozomi no sospechará nada."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:857
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b0ba41d9:

    # "It'll be a secret suggestion just for us. Okay, Hiroko?"
    "Será una sugestión secreta solo para nosotros. ¿De acuerdo, Hiroko?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:861
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e7a8dfe4:

    # ks "{cps=16}One... two, and... {/cps}{w=1.0}three."
    ks "{cps=16}Uno... dos, y... {/cps}{w=1.0}tres."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:886
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7dc95f96:

    # h uniform_headhold shocked_side "H-holy shit I can say stuff again!" with dissolve
    h uniform_headhold shocked_side "¡P-puta madre, otra vez puedo decir cosas!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:889
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_da9d9140:

    # "As Nozomi chuckles, Hiroko turns to her; the anger in her face quickly giving way to a most curious expression." with dissolve
    "Mientras Nozomi se ríe, Hiroko voltea a verla; la ira en su rostro rápidamente da lugar a una expresión de lo más curiosa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:890
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_32c153ce:

    # h "S-so like... all that just now was hypnosis? For real?"
    h "E-entonces, o sea... ¿todo eso fue hipnosis? ¿De verdad?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:891
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_35a0012a:

    # "Nozomi nods her head enthusiastically."
    "Nozomi asiente con entusiasmo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:892
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1faee75a:

    # n smile_side "Yeah. Hypnosis can be a lot of fun if you're willing to keep an open mind about it." with dissolve
    n smile_side "Sí. La hipnosis puede ser muy divertida si estás dispuesta a mantener la mente abierta. " with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:893
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5c2cbaff:

    # h nervous "Uhh, well I mean..." with dissolve
    h nervous "Emm, bueno, este..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:894
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6645230e:

    # "Hiroko shifts nervously as she glances towards the guy who just hypnotized her."
    "Los nervios de Hiroko se notan en sus movimientos al voltear a ver al tipo que acaba de hipnotizarla."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:895
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9aa1ef25:

    # "She looks confused at the sight of me now. Conflicted, even."
    "Ahora luce confundida al mirarme. Conflictuada, incluso."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:896
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_46e39d5d:

    # n smile "I thought you handled yourself really well. Didn't she, Kyou?" with dissolve
    n smile "Yo creo que lo hiciste bastante bien. ¿No es cierto, Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:903
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_20cb3fec:

    # "So what if I were to give her subconscious a little reminder of what she's supposed to think now..."
    "¿Qué tal si le doy a su subconsciente un pequeño recordatorio de lo que se supone que piense...?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:899
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_096a900a:

    # ks smile "Yeah, that went great. If I didn't know better I'd even say Hiroko might even *enjoy* being hypnotized."
    ks smile "Sí, salió genial. Si no la conociera, hasta diría que Hiroko tal vez *disfrute* ser hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:903
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e22d6ba6:

    # h uniform_headhold2 frown "{cps=16}Ehh? I don't... {/cps}{w=1.5}{nw}" with dissolve
    h uniform_headhold2 frown "{cps=16}¿Eeh? De ninguna... {/cps}{w=1.5}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:911
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a49facca:

    # extend confused "u-uuuh..."
    extend confused "e-eeeh..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:927
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3c0009ce:

    # "I watch as Hiroko frowns at me reflexively, only for her features to soften a little as she starts to seriously consider what I just said." with dissolve
    "Observo a Hiroko fruncirme reflexivamente el ceño, y luego sus facciones se suavizan un poco al empezar a considerar seriamente lo que acabo de decir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:928
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a389fd34:

    # h frown_side "Like, don't get me wrong, it was kinda shitty making me think I lost my voice an' all." with dissolve
    h frown_side "O sea, no me malentiendan, si estuvo de la mierda hacerme creer que perdí la voz y eso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:930
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_62f2f06b:

    # h confused "But besides that it was... sorta okay?" with dissolve
    h confused "Pero fuera de eso estuvo... ¿bien, supongo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:931
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7451e37f:

    # h uniform_headhold2 sleepy "I kinda... enjoyed that sleepy sorta feeling when..." with dissolve
    h uniform_headhold2 sleepy "Creo que... disfruté esa sensación de quedarme dormida cuando..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:932
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3edde4b2:

    # h confused_side "W-when he hypnotized me? So..." with dissolve
    h confused_side "¿C-cuando me hipnotizó? Así que..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:933
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7bdc2083:

    # h uniform shocked blush "F-fuck me, do I seriously ENJOY this shit?" with dissolve
    h uniform shocked blush "N-no me jodas, ¿en serio DISFRUTO esta mierda?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:934
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f8582e8c:

    # n surprised_side "Oh gosh, Hiroko, what are you saying?" with dissolve
    n surprised_side "Oh, cielos, Hiroko, ¿qué estás diciendo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:936
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_418fd7b3:

    # "Hiroko turns to Nozomi once again, like she's extremely confused by her own admission." with dissolve
    "Hiroko voltea a ver a Nozomi una vez más, como si estuviera extremadamente confundida con su propia admisión." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:937
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cddeeb15:

    # h "H'yeah, don't ask me why, but... yeah. Something about it's super agreeing with me, no doubt about that."
    h "Sí, no me preguntes por qué, pero... sí. Algo de esto me superagradó, de eso no hay duda."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:938
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d4a794e3:

    # "But confused or not, she really did confess to liking this experience. She couldn't reject the idea at all."
    "Pero confundida o no, en verdad acaba de confesar que le gustó esta experiencia. No pudo rechazar la idea."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:939
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e0275fb3:

    # h confused "Kinda makes me wanna do it again..." with dissolve
    h confused "Como que me da ganas de hacerlo otra vez..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:941
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_94f0e5ac:

    # n happy "Ehehehe, I'm so glad you're okay with this, Hiroko! Especially when you told me how nervous you were about doing this with Kyou." with dissolve
    n happy "¡Jejejeje, me alegra tanto que te haya gustado, Hiroko! Sobre todo cuando me dijiste lo nerviosa que te ponía hacer esto con Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:942
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_82a7542c:

    # "And it makes me crack another smile of my own. This is going great."
    "Y eso dibuja otra sonrisa en mi rostro. Esto está yendo genial."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:944
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_202f10bd:

    # h uniform_headhold nervous_side "H'yeah, well... I ain't gonna let you down, Nozo. Even if it means I gotta do it with this jerkoff." with dissolve
    h uniform_headhold nervous_side "Seh, bueno... No voy a defraudarte, Nozo. Aunque signifique que tengo que hacerlo con este idiota." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:945
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_978e6f1f:

    # "Still with that attitude, though. Small victories, I suppose."
    "Aunque sigue con esa actitud. Victorias pequeñas, supongo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:946
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_930c17b7:

    # ks sigh "Come on, be nice. I just gave you an *enjoyable* experience, didn't I?"
    ks sigh "Oh, por favor, sé amable. Te acabo de dar una experiencia que *disfrutaste*, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:947
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_8f5f637e:

    # h uniform_headhold2 nervous "M-mmmph..." with dissolve
    h uniform_headhold2 nervous "M-mmmf..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:949
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9f2723dc:

    # ks frown "So would it kill you to show me just a little bit of respect for once?" with dissolve
    ks frown "Así que, ¿te mataría mostrarme solo un poquito de respeto por una vez?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:952
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3af38ed3:

    # "Hiroko doesn't have a snappy comeback this time. Instead she regards me with an almost dopey expression; that inner conflict surely still raging in her confused mind." with dissolve
    "Hiroko no me da una respuesta esta vez. Solo me mira con una expresión casi embobada; ese conflicto interno sin duda resuenta con furor en su confusa mente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:953
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a6849639:

    # "So it's time I really turned the screws on her."
    "Es hora de apretarle las tuercas de verdad."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:954
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0a52322a:

    # ks frown "Hiroko, if you're serious about doing this we need to respect one another. Things could go really bad for us if we do this show and you you've got any misgivings about this."
    ks frown "Hiroko, si en serio quieres hacer esto, necesitamos respetarnos el uno al otro. Las cosas pueden salir muy mal si hacemos este espectáculo guardando desconfianzas."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:955
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ecf8047a:

    # ks "Hypnosis is a mutual collaboration between the hypnotist and the hypnotized, after all. So if you *want* me to hypnotize you again, you could stand to be a little nicer to me."
    ks "La hipnosis es una colaboración mutua entre hipnotista e hipnotizado. Así que, si *quieres* que te hipnotice otra vez, podrías al menos ser un poco más amable."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:956
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_626ef5b0:

    # h sleepy "Aaah..." with dissolve
    h sleepy "Aaah..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:957
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c8bb1604:

    # ks "I'll do my best as well. I want this show to work just as much as you guys, and we don't have time to be at each other's throats."
    ks "Yo también daré mi mayor esfuerzo. Quiero que este espectáculo funcione tanto como ustedes, y no tenemos tiempo de pelearnos entre nosotros."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:958
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_8b3d2ddf:

    # "I smile at her, in a way I hope will come off as encouraging."
    "Le sonrío intentando lucir alentador."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:959
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cf63ed98:

