    # "(( AUTHOR'S NOTE: So what follows is a short outline for how I think this one will go, with some major details still missing until I figure something out. ))"
    "(( NOTA DE LA AUTORA: Lo que sigue a continuación es un pequeño bosquejo de cómo creo que irán las cosas, faltándole aún algunos detalles grandes hasta que piense en algo. ))"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3564
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_50211edd:

    # "Kyou doesn't have it in him to cause these two any more pain. Hiroko has suffered more than enough, and to put Nozomi in harm's way and betray her trust in him? That's just unthinkable!"
    "Kyou no quiere causarles más dolor a estas dos. Hiroko ya sufrió más que suficiente, ¿y poner a Nozomi en riesgo y traicionar su confianza? ¡Eso es impensable!"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3565
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_6849fab5:

    # "So he sticks to the original plan and gives them the more playful harmless suggestions he discussed with Nozomi."
    "Así que se apega al plan original y les da la sugestión divertida e inofensiva que discutió con Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3571
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_ab6193bb:

    # "They snap to at his direction, helplessly compelled to act on his will, and it seems everyone has a good time." with dissolve
    "Despiertan a su señal y actúan conforme a su voluntad sin poder resistir, y todos la pasan muy bien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3572
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_7719c41b:

    # "When the show ends, Hiroko is happy that their show went without a hitch and Nozomi thanks Kyou for keeping his word and delivering a pleasant experience."
    "Cuando el espectáculo termina, Hiroko está feliz de que haya transcurrido sin tropiezos y Nozomi le agradece a Kyou por darles una experiencia placentera."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3574
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_04851846:

    # "But no more repeat performances! They're done with the dodgy webcam shows in front of strangers!" with dissolve
    "¡Pero no habrá más actos! ¡No más espectáculos dudosos ante la cámara frente a extraños!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3575
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_66b30dcd:

    # "Kyou has little hesitation in agreeing, as he thinks back to the temptations of before."
    "Kyou no se lo piensa mucho antes de aceptar, considerando las tentaciones de antes."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3577
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_93745da1:

    # "Hiroko expresses an interest in doing another session, though. Maybe they can get together and plan something that's just for them?" with dissolve
    "Aunque Hiroko expresa interés en hacer otra sesión. ¿Tal vez puedan juntarse y planear algo solo para ellos?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3579
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_cca0347a:

    # "However Nozomi is keen to call a rain check on that. Actually, she'd like to talk to Hiroko some about their experiences with Kyou's hypnosis up to now." with dissolve
    "Sin embargo, Nozomi rápidamente le frena los pies. De hecho, le gustaría hablar con Hiroko sobre su experiencia con la hipnosis de Kyou hasta ahora." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3582
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_77f6dcdb:

    # "Kyou sees them out while that discussion is going on and he wonders what he's going to do now his budding webcam hypnotist career is apparently over."
    "Kyou se despide de ellas mientras continúan conversando y se pregunta qué es lo que hará ahora que su naciente carrera de hipnotista de cámara web al parecer se ha acabado."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3584
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_4739fd0d:

    # "He's certainly enjoyed his time with Hiroko and Nozomi, and hopes they can meet again and talk more about their now mutual interest."
    "Ciertamente disfrutó estos momentos con Hiroko y Nozomi, y espera que puedan volver a reunirse y hablar de su recién descubierto interés mutuo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3585
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_266ef952:

    # "Maybe even practise hypnosis on them some more? But not with his penlight, surely! Not after what he now suspects about its dangerous hold on both of them."
    "¿Tal vez incluso practicar hipnosis en ellas un poco más? ¡Pero definitivamente no con su linterna! No después de lo que ahora sospecha del poder que tiene sobre ellas."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3586
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_7814341e:

    # "Will they even want to be around him without the lure of the penlight and its hypnotic compulsions?"
    "Siquiera querrán seguir cerca de él sin el encanto de la linterna y sus impulsos hipnóticos?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3587
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_2710079b:

    # "One thing's for sure, he can't tell them his suspicions about his penlight. What on earth would they think if they realized he was actually brainwashing them, accidental or not?"
    "Una cosa es segura, no puede decirles de sus sospechas sobre su linterna. ¿Qué irán a pensar si se dan cuenta de que de verdad les ha estado lavando el cerebro, accidente o no?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3588
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_37539716:

    # "He shudders at the thought. No, he'll keep that to himself and hope he can have a more meaningful relationship with the girls going forward."
    "Decide no pensar en eso. No, se guardará el secreto esperando tener una relación más significativa con las chicas a partir de ahora."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3590
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_670e101c:

    # "And now that the adrenaline of the night has cooled off, he realizes all he can do is wait and see what the future holds..."
    "Y ahora que la adrenalina e la noche se ha diluido, se da cuenta de que no puede hacer más que esperar a ver qué depara el futuro..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3593
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_212fb827:

    # "We then join Kyou about a week later."
    "Luego nos reunimos con Kyou una semana después."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3599
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_b2d40406:

    # "We see them going over some study material under the watchful eye of Sayori, having successfully goaded them all into taking some time to review their failure in the mock exams." with dissolve
    "Los vemos repasar algo de material de estudio bajo la supervisión de Sayori, quien finalmente logró convencerlos de tomarse algo de tiempo para revisar sus errores en los exámenes simulacro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3600
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_1a430cff:

    # "Everyone seems to be getting along okay as they go over a few questions, although Kyou thinks to himself that Nozomi and Hiroko haven't been very forthcoming about meeting up again."
    "Todos parecen llevarse bien mientras repasan algunas preguntas, aunque Kyou piensa que Nozomi y Hiroko están siendo algo reservadas respecto a volverse a reunir."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3601
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_7dc6ed43:

    # "Sure, the pair of them acknowledge him and make a little smalltalk, and they're together with him on this, but it certainly feels like they're avoiding talk of hypnosis now. They never bring it up."
    "Claro, reconocen su presencia y conversan un poco, y están con él en esto, pero ciertamente parece que evitan hablar sobre hipnosis. Ni siquiera mencionan el tema."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3602
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_399c7551:

    # "Sayori soon calls time on their session, citing her need to return to cram school."
    "Sayori pronto da la sesión por concluida, mencionando su necesidad de volver a los cursos nocturnos."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3605
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_7e0c1ee6:

    # "But as the others get up to leave, Kyou bites the bullet and asks Hiroko if she thought some more about what they talked about last week." with dissolve
    "Pero mientras los demás se levantan y se van, Kyou decide tomar el riesgo y preguntarle a Hiroko si pensó en lo que hablaron la semana pasada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3609
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_7aedc33e:

    # "Hiroko and Nozomi share a look, before Hiroko tells him she's sorta cooled off on the idea. Maybe some other time, yeah?" with dissolve
    "Hiroko y Nozomi intercambian miradas, y luego Kyou le dice que ya no está tan segura de la idea. Tal vez en otra ocasión, ¿sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3612
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_2b84317e:

    # "The pair then make their excuses and head out before Kyou can press her any further while Sayori looks on." with dissolve
    "Luego el par se excusa y se retira antes de que Kyou continúe presionando mientras Sayori observa todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3614
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_4062d554:

    # "\"They don't trust you.\" is Sayori's measured response as Kyou helplessly watches them leave." with dissolve
    "\"No confían en ti\" es la mesurada respuesta que ofrece Sayori mientras Kyou las mira irse." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3616
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_f91f8841:

    # "Well, Sayori has obviously heard something about Kyou from those two. What does she know?" with dissolve
    "Bueno, Sayori ciertamente a oído hablar un poco de Kyou de parte de esas dos. ¿Qué es lo que sabe?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3617
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_6992e888:

    # "No, it doesn't matter. Kyou doesn't need to query her to realize what she means, and he rushes out to give chase."
    "No, eso no importa. Kyou no necesita preguntarle para darse cuenta de a qué se refiere, y corre para alcanzarlas."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3624
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_089b5e19:

    # "Kyou stops them in the hallway and says sorry to Hiroko for his deception."
    "Kyou las detiene en el pasillo y se disculpa con Hiroko por sus engaños."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3625
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_0fc19635:

    # "He wanted to get back at her, but he took it too far in humiliating her and pushing her into those cam shows, then convincing her she liked it."
    "Quería represalia, pero lo llevó muy lejos humillándola y obligándola a hacer esos actos ante la cámara, convenciéndola de que le gustaba."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3628
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_51e5ec90:

    # "Nozomi looks to Hiroko and is basically like \"told you so.\"" with dissolve
    "Nozomi mira a Hiroko con cara de \"te lo dije\"." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3629
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_9ab6533c:

    # "They couldn't be sure before, but Nozomi had strongly suspected Hiroko had been tricked by Kyou's mind games rather than it coming from the heart. Now he's confirmed it."
    "No podían estar seguras, pero Nozomi sospechaba fuertemente que Hiroko había sido engañada por los juegos mentales de Kyou y no salía realmente de su corazón. Y ahora lo confirmó."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3632
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_fdfdb8f2:

    # "So what happens now? Hiroko's unsure how she feels, being conflicted about how Kyou genuinely helped her get her scholarship versus how he effectively tortured her for kicks." with dissolve
    "Entonces, ¿ahora qué? Hiroko no está segura de cómo sentirse, estando en conflicto ya que Kyou de verdad la ayudó a conseguir su beca, pero a la vez la torturó básicamente por diversión." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3634
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_f5272351:

    # "\"Give us space\" is the consensus reached, and Kyou begrudgingly accepts." with dissolve
    "\"Danos espacio\" es el consenso al que llegan, y Kyou acepta a regañadientes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3637
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_ea75dc65:

    # "They leave, and Kyou has to wonder if he really has blown his chances of having anything to do with those two."
    "Se van, y Kyou se pregunta si realmente echó a perder sus oportunidades de tener algo que ver con esas dos."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3638
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_4e13fd4f:

    # "They might forgive him, and he may be able to pursue his hypnosis skill from a more ethical standpoint with two people he's come to care about."
    "Puede que lo perdonen, y puede que él pueda pulir sus habilidades en la hipnosis desde un punto de vista más ético con dos personas que ahora estima."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3639
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_54be5fc5:

    # "But where he is right now, it sure feels like he's back where he started: Alone."
    "Pero donde se encuentra ahora ciertamente parece que está justo donde empezó: solo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3640
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_38e5a433:

    # "Aaaaand that's my hacky ending for this path! As we can see, there's a lot of work to be done to turn this into a finished script."
    "¡Yyyyy ese es más o menos mi final para este sendero! Como podemos ver, hay mucho trabajo que hacer para convertir esto en algo terminado."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3641
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_787ee0ee:

    # "Issue number one being to decide on a safe suggestion for the cam show right at the start of this decision point..."
    "Siendo lo número uno en la agenta decidir una sugestión segura para el acto ante la cámara que tiene lugar justo al seleccionar este camino..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3642
