    # "Among all the appropriate-seeming things that aren't much different to what I'm planning, there's quite a few x-rated stuff in there too."
    "Entre las cosas que parecen apropiadas que no son muy diferentes de lo que estoy planeado, hay unas cuantas algo subidas de tono."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3752
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_296f13c3:

    # "Almost as soon as I told everyone I wasn't taking suggestions people started logging off. We only have about half the number of viewers we started with."
    "Casi tan pronto como les dije a todos que no aceptaría sugerencias, la gente comenzó a desconectarse. Solo nos queda más o menos la mitad del número de espectadores que teníamos al principio."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3772
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_1d971cc5:

    # n "So, um... I guess all things considered, that went sort of okay?"
    n "Pues, em... supongo que, a pesar de todo, ¿salió más o menos bien?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3787
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_3ef9cc2c:

    # n front2 neutral "In any case... Kyou?" with dissolve
    n front2 neutral "En todo caso... ¿Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3789
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_b84aa238:

    # ks casual neutral "Yeah, what's up?" with dissolve
    ks casual neutral "¿Sí, qué pasa?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3791
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_bd78a20b:

    # n sigh "Thanks. For keeping the show clean, I mean." with dissolve
    n sigh "Gracias. Por mantener el espectáculo limpio, quiero decir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3793
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_717ca578:

    # n neutral_left "You know I had a ton of reservations about all of this. And knowing so many people were watching us the whole time is still kinda nuts." with dissolve
    n neutral_left "Sabes que tenía mis dudas respecto a todo esto. Y sabiendo que tanta gente nos estuvo mirando todo el tiempo me sigue pareciendo una locura." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3795
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_c585d37a:

    # n smile "But I'll admit it wasn't as bad as I thought, and we did have a good time. So thanks for keeping your word." with dissolve
    n smile "Pero debo admitir que no estuvo tan mal como pensé, y sí nos la pasamos bien. Así que gracias por mantener tu palabra." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3796
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_a88c3cf4:

    # "She smiles, and I smile back at her."
    "Ella sonríe, y yo le devuelvo la sonrisa."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3797
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_75228994:

    # ks smile "Yeah. No problem."
    ks smile "Sí. No hay problema."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3799
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_73efbf7e:

    # n frown "But no more repeat performances, okay? You've roped us into doing your webcam shows for the last time." with dissolve
    n frown "Pero ya no habrá más, ¿sí? Nos arrastraste a tus transmisiones en línea por última vez." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3800
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_52d00d7b:

    # ks sigh "Sure. I think I've pushed my luck with you girls enough."
    ks sigh "Seguro. Creo que ya tenté mi suerte lo suficiente con ustedes."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3802
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_b63d719a:

    # "Not like I was going to anyway, not with what I've learned tonight. Although I notice Hiroko giving me a curious look." with dissolve
    "Y no iba a hacerlo de todos modos, no con lo que aprendí esta noche. Aunque noto a Hiroko dándome una mirada curiosa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3803
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_64bb371f:

    # ks neutral "Hiroko? You got something to say?"
    ks neutral "¿Hiroko? ¿Tienes algo que decir?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3805
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_c547a8fb:

    # h dungaree_headhold2 rolleyes "I mean yeah, I'm kinda done with the camgirl shit too, but we still had fun so like..." with dissolve
    h dungaree_headhold2 rolleyes "Pues, bueno, sí, yo también estoy algo harta de la mierda esta de la cámara, pero aun así nos divertimos, así que..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3807
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_41e5d0f2:

    # h happy_closed "Maybe we could still do some more of this hypno stuff? I mean like, just the three of us?" with dissolve
    h happy_closed "¿Tal vez aún podamos hacer más cosas con hipnosis? O sea, ¿solo nosotros tres?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3808
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_9d6385eb:

    # ks smile "Ah, well..."
    ks smile "Ah, bueno..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3810
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_69e21f86:

    # n side sad_closed "Ah, let's put a pin in that one, Hiroko." with dissolve
    n side sad_closed "Ah, discutiremos eso luego, Hiroko." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3812
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_bed36f0b:

    # h sad_side "Aww, seriously? What's the matter now?" with dissolve
    h sad_side "Ayy, ¿en serio? ¿Y ahora qué pasa?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3814
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_8bf12389:

    # n neutral_side "Actually, I was hoping we could talk some more about... about all of this? I think with all our experience with hypnosis we have a lot to discuss." with dissolve
    n neutral_side "De hecho, esperaba que pudiéramos hablar un poco sobre... ¿sobre todo esto? Creo que, con toda nuestra experiencia con hipnosis, tenemos mucho que discutir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3816
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_f906e33d:

    # h smile_side "Heh, yeah we do. 'Specially now you got a feel for what he can do now, don'tcha?" with dissolve
    h smile_side "Je, vaya que sí. Sobre todo ahora que tuviste una probadita de lo que puede hacer, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3818
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_48f2ca5b:

    # n smile_side "Yeah. I suppose I do. Let's talk on the way home, okay?" with dissolve
    n smile_side "Sí. Supongo que sí. Hablemos de camino a casa, ¿de acuerdo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3821
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_d09a1d8f:

    # "I see them out while they start an animated discussion among themselves, while I'm once more alone."
    "Las veo retirarse mientras comienzan una animada conversación entre ellas, mientras yo me quedo solo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3822
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_19e99558:

    # "And I guess I need to have a discussion of my own, with myself."
    "Y creo que yo también necesito tener una discusión, conmigo mismo."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3824
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_33500d0f:

    # "What am I going to do now that my budding webcam hypnosist career is apparently over already?"
    "¿Qué voy a hacer ahora que mi naciente carrera de hipnotista de cámara web al parecer ya ha acabado?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3825
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_55b22660:

    # "The adrenaline of the night is already starting to wane, and it leaves me wanting more."
    "La adrenalina de la noche ya comienza a menguarse, y me deja deseando más."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3828
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_dd40299f:

    # "And with this penlight I could have it. Nothing could've made me more sure of that than what happened tonight."
    "Y con esta linterna, podría tenerla. Nada podría evitar que tenga lo que tuve esta noche."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3829
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_b5856ddd:

    # "I kept them safe, kept my word, but it really did feel like I could've broken it so easily. I could've made them do anything I wanted in front of that camera..."
    "Las mantuve a salvo, mantuve mi palabra, pero de verdad sentí que podría haberla roto con mucha facilidad. Pude haber logrado que hicieran lo que quisiera frente a la cámara..."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3831
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_5ed1cb01:

    # "But no, I have to be strong. I have to never use this damn thing again; certainly not on those two."
    "Pero no, tengo que ser fuerte. Nunca tengo que volver a usar esta maldita cosa; ciertamente no en ellas dos."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3832
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_352260c4:

    # "They'll understand if I want to try other methods, right? They'll want to be around me after tonight... right?"
    "Entenderán si quiero probar otros métodos, ¿cierto? Querrán seguir pasando tiempo conmigo después de esta noche... ¿cierto?"

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3833
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_c7561732:

    # "Hypnosis has been a wonderful thing to bring us together."
    "La hipnosis ha sido algo maravilloso para unirnos."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3834
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_fd509085:

    # "Maybe I abused that at first, certainly I impressed that interest on Hiroko, awakened something in her that wasn't there before."
    "Tal vez lo abusé al principio, ciertamente yo implanté ese interés en Hiroko, desperté algo en ella que no estaba ahí antes."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3835
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_ac39d9b7:

    # "But I can do better for them. For Hiroko."
    "Pero puedo hacer las cosas mejor por ellas. Por Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3836
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_b0c4d388:

    # "Yeah, if I'm going to hypnotize Hiroko and Nozomi again, I'm going to do it right. I'll learn another way. I will."
    "Sí, si voy a hipnotizar a Hiroko y a Nozomi otra vez, voy a hacerlo bien. Aprenderé otro método. Eso es lo que haré."

# game/Kyou 10.rpy:3839
translate spanish Day10_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Trickster_edf2f9da:

    # "We'll be together again..."
    "Estaremos juntos otra vez..."
